et%20some%20of%20the%20ex-president's%20highest-profile%20critics%20should%20he%20secure%20a%20second%20term%20next%20year%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2F11%2F05%2Ftrump-revenge-second-term%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20%E2%80%94%20the%20frontrunner%20in%20the%20GOP%20presidential%20primary%20who%20has%20continually%20railed%20against%20his%20loss%20to%20now-President%20Joe%20Biden%20in%20the%202020%20election%20%E2%80%94%20has%20privately%20told%20advisors%20and%20close%20allies%20this%20year%20that%20he'd%20like%20to%20see%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20probe%20individuals%20who%20railed%20against%20his%20first%20administration%2C%20per%20the%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20of%20the%20names%20that%20were%20brought%20up%20by%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20according%20to%20individuals%20who%20remained%20anonymous%20in%20the%20report%20%E2%80%94%20include%20former%20White%20House%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20John%20Kelly%2C%20former%20US%20Attorney%20General%20Bill%20Barr%2C%20ex-Trump%20administration%20attorney%20Ty%20Cobb%2C%20and%20Gen.%20Mark%20Milley%2C%20the%20former%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Joint%20Chiefs%20of%20Staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20also%20floated%20the%20prosecutions%20of%20individuals%20at%20the%20FBI%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20which%20he%20has%20railed%20against%20as%20he%20faces%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-indictment-total-charges-counts-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E91%20felony%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20four%20criminal%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20Post%2C%20Trump's%20associates%20are%20also%20mapping%20out%20ways%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Euse%20the%20Insurrection%20Act%20at%20the%20start%20of%20a%20potential%20second%20term%2C%20which%20would%20give%20him%20the%20ability%20to%20use%20military%20forces%20to%20quell%20civil%20unrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20associates%20have%20also%20been%20devising%20ways%20to%20toss%20aside%20long-standing%20policies%20to%20block%20criminal%20prosecutions%20from%20being%20influenced%20by%20politics.%20A%20defining%20hallmark%20of%20the%20Justice%20Department%20is%20its%20independence%20from%20the%20White%20House%2C%20so%20any%20attempt%20to%20use%20the%20department%20to%20enact%20political%20vengeance%20would%20ring%20major%20alarm%20bells%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20set%20of%20plans%20being%20unofficially%20mapped%20out%20has%20been%20called%20%26quot%3BProject%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20the%20plans%20have%20blasted%20the%20implications%20of%20the%20far-reaching%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20resemble%20a%20banana%20republic%20if%20people%20came%20into%20office%20and%20started%20going%20after%20their%20opponents%20willy-nilly%2C%26quot%3B%20University%20of%20Virginia%20School%20of%20Law%20professor%20Saikrishna%20Prakash%20told%20the%20Post.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20hardly%20something%20we%20should%20aspire%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkinzinger-john-kelly-trump-white-house-advisor-breakfast-afghanistan-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAfter%20Kelly%20left%20the%20White%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Econfirmed%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eseveral%20allegations%20leveled%20against%20Trump%20in%202020%2C%20including%20that%20the%20then-president%20had%20spoken%20negatively%20about%20veterans%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20clashed%20with%20Barr%20over%20the%202020%20presidential%20election%20results%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarr-trump-2020-presidential-election-not-stolen-voting-integrity-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20ex-attorney%20general%3C%2Fa%3E%20arguing%20that%20he%20could%20not%20verify%20any%20mass%20voter%20fraud%20that%20year.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-milley-court-martialed-fears-of-potential-coup-election-military-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20former%20president%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20said%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Blost%20total%20confidence%26quot%3B%20in%20Milley%20while%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECobb%20earlier%20this%20year%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-trump-lawyer-predicts-former-president-will-go-jail-cnn-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bwill%20go%20to%20jail%26quot%3B%20over%20his%20handling%20of%20classified%20documents%20which%20were%20retrieved%20from%20his%20Mar-a-Lago%20estate%20during%20a%20high-profile%20FBI%20search%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Trump%20campaign%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-presidential-justice-department-probes-barr-kelly-milley-cobb-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699226682000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6548168c3cc84b4dfafcbe8c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-presidential-justice-department-probes-barr-kelly-milley-cobb-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20associates%20have%20also%20mapped%20out%20ways%20to%20turn%20to%20the%20Insurrection%20Act%20at%20the%20start%20of%20a%20potential%20second%20term%2C%20per%20The%20Washington%20Post.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20L.%20Dorman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-presidential-justice-department-probes-barr-kelly-milley-cobb-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20%E2%80%