nk%20I%20would%20have%20to%20write%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20president%20of%20my%20alma%20mater%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20her%20actions%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Bill%20Ackman%20(%40BillAckman)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBillAckman%2Fstatus%2F1720987581549080965%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20to%20student%20Slack%20message%20boards%20being%20%26quot%3Breplete%20with%20antisemitic%20statements%2C%20memes%2C%20and%20images.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20cited%20as%20a%20problem%20pro-Palestinian%20protesters%20on%20campus%20who%20chanted%2C%20%26quot%3BIntifada!%20Intifada!%20Intifada!%20From%20the%20River%20to%20the%20Sea%2C%20Palestine%20Shall%20Be%20Free!%26quot%3B%C2%A0%26quot%3BIntifada%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20reference%20to%20previous%20Palestinian%20uprisings%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20is%20surrounded%20by%20Israeli%20and%20Egyptian%20military%20forces%20that%20have%20for%20decades%20controlled%20who%20%E2%80%94and%20what%20%E2%80%94%20can%20come%20and%20go%20from%20the%20tiny%20sliver%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAckman%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-ackman-harvard-release-names-students-blaming-israel-violence-hamas-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecalled%20on%20the%20university%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20publicly%20release%20the%20names%20of%20the%20students%20who%20had%20signed%20a%20letter%20critical%20of%20Israel%20in%20the%20days%20following%20Hamas'%20terrorist%20attacks%20on%20October%207%20to%20ensure%20that%20CEO's%20wouldn't%20%26quot%3Binadvertently%20hire%26quot%3B%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20latest%20missive%2C%20Ackman%20urged%20Gay%20to%20take%20immediate%20action%20to%20address%20the%20outburst%20of%20activities%20critical%20of%20Israel%20on%20campus%2C%20noting%20that%20her%20initial%20%26quot%3Bfailure%20to%20condemn%26quot%3B%20Hamas'%20October%207%20terrorist%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20had%20%26quot%3Bopened%20the%20door%20for%20a%20wave%20of%20anti-Israel%20attacks%20on%20campus%20that%20have%20led%20to%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20antisemitic%20protests%20and%20actions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20recently%2C%20Harvard%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20extremely%20comfortable%20place%20to%20be%20Jewish%20and%2For%20Israeli%2C%26quot%3B%20Ackman%20wrote%2C%20noting%20that%20his%20daughter%2C%20who%20graduated%20from%20the%20university%20in%202020%2C%20said%20that%20antisemitism%20was%20%26quot%3Bnonexistent%26quot%3B%20during%20her%20time%20on%20campus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAckman%20outlined%20seven%20steps%20for%20Gay's%20administration%20in%20his%20letter%20that%20included%20immediately%20suspending%20the%20students%20who%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hbs.edu%2Fabout%2Fleadership%2Fstatements-and-speeches%2FPages%2Four-values.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Everbally%20and%20physically%20assaulted%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20Israeli%20student%20in%20his%20first%20year%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School.%20He%20called%20for%20the%20protesters%20chanting%20%26quot%3BIntifada%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20subject%20to%20disciplinary%20action%20and%20for%20the%20university%20to%20review%20its%20Slack%20message%20boards%20and%20refer%20students%20who%20made%20anti-Israel%20or%20pro-Palestinian%20remarks%20for%20disciplinary%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20urged%20the%20university%20to%20%26quot%3Bpublicly%20reach%20out%26quot%3B%20to%20students%20to%20gather%20and%20investigate%20any%20examples%20of%20antisemitic%20acts%20%E2%80%94%20and%20take%20disciplinary%20action%20if%20necessary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAckman%20also%20asked%20for%20a%20task%20force%20to%20be%20created%20to%20review%20the%20actions%20of%20Harvard's%20Office%20of%20Equity%2C%20Diversity%2C%20Inclusion%2C%20and%20Belonging%20and%20to%20publicize%20the%20results%20to%20better%20understand%20%26quot%3Bthe%20so