aza%20Strip%20Into%20Two%2C%20Says%20Israel%20Amid%20%26quot%3BSignificant%20Strikes%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20said%20Sunday%20it%20was%20pounding%20Gaza%20with%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%26quot%3B%20strikes%20after%20cutting%20it%20in%20two%2C%20as%20America's%20top%20diplomat%20pressed%20a%20Middle%20East%20tour%20focused%20on%20humanitarian%20aid%20for%20the%20Palestinians.%20Israeli%20forces%20%26quot%3Bhave%20encircled%20Gaza%20City...%20Now%20there%20exists%20a%20south%20Gaza%20and%20a%20north%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20army%20spokesman%20Daniel%20Hagari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20spoke%20after%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20visited%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%2C%20Iraq%20and%20Cyprus%20Sunday%20on%20a%20whirlwind%20tour%20with%20the%20focus%20on%20aid%20for%20beleaguered%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20and%20preventing%20attacks%20by%20Iran-backed%20groups%20on%20American%20troops%20in%20response%20to%20Israel's%20Gaza%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken%20met%20Palestinian%20president%20Mahmud%20Abbas%20who%20denounced%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bgenocide%26quot%3B%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20the%20health%20ministry%20in%20the%20Hamas-run%20territory%20said%20at%20least%209%2C770%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20had%20been%20killed%20in%20more%20than%20four%20weeks%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20telecommunications%20in%20Gaza%20cut%20for%20a%20third%20time%2C%20Washington%20rebuffed%20calls%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20backed%20Israel's%20goal%20of%20crushing%20Hamas%20who%20staged%20the%20worst%20attack%20in%20the%20country's%20history%20on%20October%207%2C%20killing%20more%20than%201%2C400%20people%2C%20also%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20and%20taking%20over%20240%20hostages%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGlobal%20concern%20has%20soared%20over%20the%20spiralling%20Gaza%20death%20toll%2C%20but%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20again%20vowed%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20won't%20be%20a%20ceasefire%20until%20the%20hostages%20are%20returned%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20them%20remove%20this%20from%20their%20lexicon.%20We%20are%20saying%20this%20to%20our%20enemies%20and%20to%20our%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20veteran%20right-wing%20premier%20said%20after%20meeting%20troops%20at%20an%20air%20force%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20simply%20continue%20until%20we%20win.%20We%20have%20no%20alternative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoldiers%20engaged%20in%20house-to-house%20combat%20on%20Sunday%20as%20tanks%20and%20armoured%20bulldozers%20churned%20through%20the%20sand%20in%20footage%20released%20by%20the%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20strike%20is%20like%20an%20earthquake%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaza%20City%20resident%20Alaa%20Abu%20Hasera%20said%20in%20a%20devastated%20area%20where%20entire%20blocks%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken%2C%20in%20his%20talks%20with%20Abbas%2C%20said%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20%26quot%3Bmust%20not%20be%20forcibly%20displaced%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20US%20State%20Department%20spokesman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20distributed%20leaflets%20and%20sent%20text%20messages%20urging%20Palestinian%20civilians%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20to%20head%20south%2C%20but%20a%20US%20official%20said%20Saturday%20at%20least%20350%2C000%20civilians%20remained%20in%20what%20is%20now%20an%20urban%20war%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbbas%20denounced%20%26quot%3Bthe%20genocide%20and%20destruction%20suffered%20by%20our%20Palestinian%20people%20in%20Gaza%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Israel's%20war%20machine%2C%20with%20no%20regard%20for%20the%20principles%20of%20international%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20Palestinian%20news%20agency%20Wafa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Stop%20extremist%20violence'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20relentlessly%20pounded%20Gaza%20in%20its%20battle%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%2C%20levelling%20entire%20city%20blocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20parents%20in%20Gaza%20do%20not%20know%20whether%20they%20can%20feed%20their%20children%20today%20and%20whether%20they%20will%20even%20survive%20to%20see%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cindy%20McCain%2C%20head%20of%20the%20World%20Food%20Programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken%20last%20week%20told%20a%20Senate%20hearing%20Abbas's%20Palestinian%20Authority%20(PA)%20should%20retake%20control%20of%20Gaza%20after%20the%20war.%20It%20currently%20exercises%20only%20limited%20autonomy%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Netanyahu%20has%20long%20sought%20to%20sideline%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbbas%20said%20Sunday%20the%20PA%20could%20return%20to%20power%20in%20Gaza%20in%20the%20future%20only%20if%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensive%20political%20solution%26quot%3B%20is%20found%20for%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWashington%20has%20said%20it%20backs%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20alongside%20Israel%2C%20but%20Netanyahu's%20hard-right%20government%20has%20been%20implacably%20opposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20has%20exacerbated%20tensions%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20where%20more%20than%20150%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20clashes%20with%20Israeli%20forces%20and%20in%20settler%20attacks%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken%20and%20Abbas%20discussed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20need%20to%20stop%20extremist%20violence%20against%20Palestinians%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20the%20State%20Department%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'We%20saw%20dead%20bodies'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20Israel%20sent%20ground%20forces%20into%20the%20north%20of%20Gaza%20late%20last%20month%2C%20%26quot%3Bover%202%2C500%20terror%20targets%20have%20been%20struck%26quot%3B%20by%20%26quot%3Bground%2C%20air%20and%20naval%20forces%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20army%20said%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPhone%20and%20internet%20connections%20were%20down%20for%20the%20third%20time%20during%20the%20war%2C%20according%20to%20Paltel%2C%20the%20last%20remaining%20major%20operator.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20blackout%2C%20the%20Israeli%20army%20launched%20its%20intense%20bombardment%20on%20Gaza%20City%20and%20other%20nearby%20zones%20in%20the%20territory's%20north.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20explosions%20were%20so%20powerful%20they%20could%20be%20heard%20in%20Rafah%20in%20the%20far%20south%2C%20an%20AFP%20journalist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20said%20Israel%20was%20carrying%20out%20%26quot%3Bintense%20bombings%26quot%3B%20around%20several%20hospitals%20in%20northern%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImages%20showed%20civilians%20heading%20south%20away%20from%20the%20fighting%2C%20though%20military%20spokesman%20Hagari%20told%20foreign%20reporters%20Hamas%20was%20using%20roadblocks%20to%20try%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20fleeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20dead%20bodies%20in%20the%20streets%2C%26quot%3B%20Suhad%20Zorob%20said%20as%20she%20fled%20south.%20%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20the%20tanks...%20only%20one%20street%20away%20from%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%20said%20Israeli%20bombing%20of%20Al-Maghazi%20refugee%20camp%20late%20Saturday%20killed%2045%20people%2C%20with%20an%20eyewitness%20reporting%20children%20dead%20and%20homes%20smashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20Israeli%20air%20strike%20targeted%20my%20neighbours'%20house%20in%20Al-Maghazi%20camp%2C%20my%20house%20next%20door%20partially%20collapsed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mohammed%20Alaloul%2C%2037%2C%20a%20journalist%20working%20for%20the%20Turkish%20Anadolu%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20AFP%20the%20bombing%20killed%20four%20of%20his%20children%2C%20four%20of%20his%20brothers%20and%20several%20of%20his%20nieces%20and%20nephews.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20has%20said%20it%20is%20looking%20into%20whether%20its%20forces%20were%20operating%20in%20the%20area%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20bombing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken%20faced%20a%20rising%20tide%20of%20anger%20in%20meetings%20with%20Arab%20foreign%20ministers%20in%20Jordan%20on%20Saturday%2C%20where%20he%20reaffirmed%20US%20support%20for%20%26quot%3Bhumanitarian%20pauses%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20a%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20US%20ambassador%20to%20Israel%2C%20Jack%20Lew%2C%20said%20Sunday%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attack%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20stain%20on%20humanity%20that%20cannot%20happen%20again%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Not%20a%20war%2C%20a%20massacre'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20visiting%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20Blinken%20made%20a%20brief%20stop%20in%20Cyprus%2C%20the%20nearest%20EU%20member%20state%2C%20which%20has%20said%20it%20is%20working%20towards%20establishing%20a%20maritime%20corridor%20for%20aid%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20flew%20to%20Baghdad%20and%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Mohamed%20Shia%20al-Sudani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20made%20very%20clear%20that%20attacks%20or%20threats%20coming%20from%20militias%20that%20are%20aligned%20with%20Iran%20are%20totally%20unacceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20Blinken%20said%20in%20Baghdad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%20Blinken%20was%20expected%20in%20Turkey%2C%20whose%20President%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan%20has%20held%20Netanyahu%20personally%20responsible%20for%20Gaza's%20growing%20civilian%20death%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETurkey%20on%20Saturday%20said%20it%20was%20recalling%20its%20ambassador%20to%20Israel%20and%20breaking%20off%20contacts%20with%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInternational%20concern%20mounted%20over%20the%20suffering.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrench%20Foreign%20Minister%20Catherine%20Colonna%2C%20visiting%20Qatar%2C%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Ban%20immediate%2C%20durable%20and%20observed%20humanitarian%20truce%26quot%3B%20that%20could%20%26quot%3Blead%20to%20a%20ceasefire%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EForeign%20Minister%20Sameh%20Shoukry%20of%20Egypt%2C%20which%20has%20been%20acting%20as%20the%20sole%20conduit%20for%20foreigners%20to%20escape%20Gaza%20and%20for%20aid%20to%20get%20in%2C%20on%20Saturday%20called%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20and%20comprehensive%20ceasefire%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20call%20was%20echoed%20by%20thousands%20of%20protesters%20in%20Washington%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Palestinians%2C%20one%20of%20multiple%20rallies%20held%20from%20Indonesia%20to%20Iran%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20European%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThousands%20also%20demonstrated%20in%20Israel%20on%20Saturday%20as%20pressure%20mounts%20on%20Netanyahu%20over%20his%20government's%20lack%20of%20preparedness%20for%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20and%20its%20handling%20of%20the%20hostage%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHundreds%20outside%20Netanyahu's%20Jerusalem%20residence%20calling%20on%20him%20to%20resign%2C%20while%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20relatives%20and%20friends%20of%20some%20of%20the%20hostages%20chanted%20%26quot%3Bbring%20them%20home%20now%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699219080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fqvvaaq5_gaza-strip-afp_625x300_06_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcut-gaza-strip-into-two-says-israel-amid-significant-strikes-4548657%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Israeli%20army%20said%20its%20land%20assault%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20had%20on%20Sunday%20split%20the%20Palestinian%20territory%20in%20two%2C%20with%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%26quot%3B%20strikes%20continuing%20in%20its%20war%20against%20Hamas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcut-gaza-strip-into-two-says-israel-amid-significant-strikes-4548657%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2