articleshow%2F104992769.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104992769.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAthiya%20Shetty%20turned%2031%20on%20November%205%20and%20the%20actress%20got%20a%20mushy%20birthday%20wish%20from%20husband%20KL%20Rahul.%20She%20reacts%20to%20him%20and%20expresses%20that%20she's%20missing%20him!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkl-rahul-drops-mushy-post-for-athiya-shetty-suniel-shetty-arjun-kapoor-react-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F104992769.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20middle-schooler%20just%20won%20%2425%2C000%20for%20inventing%20a%20fire-detection%20device%20that%20works%20faster%20than%20the%20average%20smoke%20detector%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shanya%20Gill%20posing%20with%20an%20award.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6547b498b788914e55508711%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221950%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShanya%20Gill%20won%20%2425%2C000%20for%20her%20fire%20detection%20device.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Society%20for%20Science%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E12-year-old%20Shanya%20Gill%20won%20a%20national%20science%20competition%20for%20her%20fire%20detection%20device.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20device%20works%20quicker%20than%20the%20average%20smoke%20detector%20by%20using%20a%20thermal%20camera.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGill%20said%20she%20hopes%20to%20use%20the%20%2425%2C000%20prize%20to%20take%20her%20device%20to%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20sixth%20grader%20Shanya%20Gill%20and%20her%20family%20were%20shocked%20to%20hear%20a%20restaurant%20behind%20their%20house%20had%20burned%20to%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20really%20moving%20for%20my%20family%20because%20it%20was%20something%20that%20we%20had%20never%20really%20experienced%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Gill%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20inspired%20her%20to%20create%20a%20fire-detection%20device%20that%20could%20identify%20fires%20faster%20than%20an%20average%20smoke%20detector%20and%20send%20a%20text%20to%20users%20to%20alert%20them%20of%20a%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20she's%20hoping%20to%20take%20the%20device%20to%20market%20after%20judges%20at%20the%20Thermo%20Fisher%20Scientific%20Junior%20Innovators%20Challenge%20awarded%20her%20the%20top%20prize%20out%20of%2065%2C000%20middle%20schoolers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGill's%20fire%20detector%20uses%20thermal%20imaging%2C%20rather%20than%20smoke%20detection%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGill's%20device%20uses%20two%20key%20components%3A%20a%20thermal%20camera%20and%20a%20Raspberry%20Pi%2C%20which%20is%20a%20small%20single-board%20computer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20coded%20the%20Raspberry%20Pi%20with%20Python%20and%20the%20thermal%20camera%20gives%20images%20to%20the%20Raspberry%20Pi%20to%20analyze%2C%26quot%3B%20Gill%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20purpose%20of%20the%20device%20is%20to%20detect%20an%20unattended%20fire%20and%20send%20a%20text%20message%20to%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20computer%20differentiates%20between%20thermal%20readings%20moving%20horizontally%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20a%20person%20or%20an%20animal%20%E2%80%94%20and%20thermal%20readings%20traveling%20vertically%2C%20such%20as%20smoke%20rising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe's%20got%20a%20really%20interesting%20device.%20I%20mean%2C%20it%20detects%20fires%20earlier%20than%20smoke%20detectors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Maya%20Ajmera%2C%20president%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%20of%20the%20Society%20for%20Science%2C%20an%20organizing%20partner%20of%20the%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shanya%20Gill%20holding%20up%20her%20device%20in%20front%20of%20a%20research%20poster.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6547dc7e36d588dc55cb1552%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGill's%20device%20has%20two%20main%20components%3A%20a%20thermal%20camera%20and%20a%20small%20computer.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Society%20for%20Science%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGill%20said%20she%20plans%20to%20use%20the%20money%20to%20take%20her%20detector%20to%20market%20%E2%80%94%20and%20any%20leftover%20funds%20will%20go%20to%20charities%20that%20help%20people%20affected%20by%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20definitely%20want%20to%20put%20some%20in%20some%20charities%20that%20help%20people%20that%20may%20have%20gotten%20their%20homes%20destroyed%20by%20fires%2C%20because%20that's%20really%20just%20my%20whole%20purpose%20of%20this%20project%3A%20For%20this%20invention%20to%20reach%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible%20and%20to%20also%20save%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible%20and%20rebuild%20the%20things%20that%20people%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20Gill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECompetition%20officials%20say%20Gill%20stood%20out%20for%20her%20innovative%20project%2C%20collaborative%20spirit%2C%20and%20leadership%20skills%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E65%2C000%20middle%20schoolers%20initially%20entered%20the%20competition%20and%20competed%20regionally.%20Of%20those%20students%2C%20roughly.%20Some%206%2C000%20were%20nominated%20to%20move%20to%20the%20national%20competition%2C%20and%20about%202%2C000%20typically%20go%20through%20with%20applying%20to%20compete%2C%20according%20to%20Ajmera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20rounds%20of%20judging%2C%20the%20pools%20shrinks%20to%2030%20top%20finalists%20who%20go%20on%20to%20attend%20the%20national%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fregeneron-international-science-fair-high-school-students-school-shootings-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escience%20fair%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20Gill%20and%20her%20fellow%20finalists%20were%20in%20the%20top%20.04%25%20of%20students%20who%20competed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAjmera%20told%20Insider%20the%2030%20finalists%20were%20judged%20on%20two%20factors%3A%20the%20projects%20themselves%20and%20a%20series%20of%20surprise%20challenges%20they%20completed%20in%20pre-assigned%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20challenges%20and%20throughout%20the%20competition%2C%20what%20we%20understand%20is%20she%20exhibited%20leadership%2C%20collaboration%2C%20she%20exhibited%20grace%2C%20and%20critical%20thinking%20skills%2C%26quot%3B%20Ajmera%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExpert%20practitioners%20judged%20the%20students%20in%20the%20STEM%20field%2C%20Ajmera%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20not%20only%20had%20a%20brilliant%20project%20but%20just%20carried%20those%20leadership%20and%20collaboration%20skills%20and%20her%20challenges%20and%20stood%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Ajmera%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20wait%20to%20see%20what%20her%20journey%20looks%20like%20over%20the%20next%2010%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshanya-gill-thermo-fisher-science-fair-winner-fire-detection-system-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699209684000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6547b498b788914e55508711%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshanya-gill-thermo-fisher-science-fair-winner-fire-detection-system-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2212-year-old%20Shanya%20Gill%20invented%20a%20fire%20detection%20system%20that%20works%20faster%20than%20the%20average%20smoke%20detector.%20She%20says%20she%20will%20use%20her%20prize%20money%20to%20take%20her%20product%20to%20market.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22khawkinson%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Hawkinson%20)%22%2C%22enga