ctive%20agreement%20with%20Tesla%2C%20it%20was%20left%20with%20no%20other%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifmetall.se%2Faktuellt%2Ftesla%2Fbackground-information-on-if-metalls-conflict-at-tesla%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20website%2C%20the%20union%20said%20it%20wanted%20%26quot%3Bour%20members%20at%20Tesla%20to%20have%20the%20same%20decent%20and%20safe%20working%20conditions%20as%20the%20members%20at%20other%20similar%20companies%20in%20Sweden.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%2090%25%20of%20Sweden's%20employees%20are%20covered%20by%20collective%20agreements%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F11%2F05%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Ftesla-sweden-unions.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20The%20agreements%20allow%20labor%20conditions%20and%20wages%20to%20be%20negotiated%20between%20unions%20and%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIF%20Metall%20is%20seeking%20to%20set%20a%20basis%20for%20wages%20and%20benefits%20for%20the%20roughly%20120%20employees%20who%20work%20at%20Tesla%20service%20facilities%20in%20Sweden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20Tesla%20employees%20are%20participating%20in%20the%20strikes%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwedish%20dockworkers%20have%20also%20said%20they%20would%20support%20the%20action%20and%20block%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.transport.se%2Fpublicerat%2Fsympati-for-if-metall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eall%20deliveries%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Teslas%20from%20being%20unloaded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dockworkers%20do%20not%20directly%20work%20for%20Tesla%2C%20but%20control%20the%20four%20major%20ports%20that%20the%20EVs%20can%20enter%20the%20country%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20from%20Tesla%20have%20agreed%20to%20meet%20with%20the%20union%20on%20Monday%2C%20a%20union%20official%20said%2C%20per%20The%20NYT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nordic%20country%20is%20one%20of%20T