v%20accused%20it%20of%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bcunning%26quot%3B%20party%2C%20accused%20it%20of%20%26quot%3Bbetraying%26quot%3B%20him%2C%20and%20urged%20the%20people%20to%20not%20vote%20for%20its%20leaders%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20not%20vote%20for%20the%20Congress.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20cunning%20party.%20It%20is%20now%20being%20supportive%20of%20the%20caste%20census%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20votes.%20If%20It%20has%20betrayed%20us%2C%20how%20come%20the%20public%20is%20significant%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20at%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Jatara%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20also%20said%20that%20by%20the%20time%20the%20general%20election%20of%202024%20approaches%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20also%20come%20in%20support%20of%20caste-based%20census%20because%20it's%20the%20demand%20of%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20addressing%20the%20public%20rally%2C%20the%20SP%20chief%20also%20targeted%20the%20present%20government%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20over%20poor%20infrastructure%20and%20women's%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20PM%20Modi's%20free%20ration%20scheme%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20getting%20nothing%20as%20ration%2C%20then%20why%20will%20you%20vote%20for%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20slammed%20the%20BJP%20by%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bloot-%3Cem%3Etantrik%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20is%20on%20a%20three-day%20visit%20to%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%C2%A0The%20Samajwadi%20Party%20has%20fielded%20candidates%20on%2072%20seats%20in%20the%20upcoming%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20strained%20partners%20in%20the%20I.N.D.I.A.%20bloc%20have%20been%20at%20loggerheads%20following%20the%20breakdown%20in%20seat-sharing%20talks%2C%20with%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20firing%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Echirkut%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(small-timer)%20jibe%20at%20Congress'%20UP%20chief%20Ajay%20Rai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUpset%20over%20the%20Congress's%20alleged%20seat%20snub%20to%20the%20SP%20ahead%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20Congress%2C%20don't%20let%20your%20%3Cem%3Echirkut%3C%2Fem%3E%20leaders%20talk%20about%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20clueless%20whether%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(I.N.D.I.A.)%20was%20meant%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20at%20the%20national%20or%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Congress%20didn't%20want%20to%20give%20us%20seats%20(in%20Madhya%20Pradesh)%2C%20they%20could%20have%20said%20so%20before.%20We%20have%20decided%20to%20go%20alone%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20After%20(the%20breakdown%20in%20seat-sharing%20talks%20in)%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20I%20have%20come%20to%20realise%20that%20I.N.D.I.A.%20is%20meant%20only%20for%20the%20general%20elections.%20But%20if%20Congress%20continues%20to%20behave%20like%20this%2C%20then%20who%20will%20stand%20with%20them%3F%20If%20we%20fight%20against%20the%20BJP%20with%20such%20confusion%20and%20doubts%20in%20our%20minds%20(around%20the%20alliance)%2C%20we%20will%20never%20succeed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Ajay%20Rai%20earlier%20asked%20the%20SP%20to%20withdraw%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20as%20the%20Akhilesh%20Yadav-led%20party%2C%20he%20said%2C%20did%20not%20have%20any%20base%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20(Akhilesh%20Yadav)%20are%20a%20part%20of%20the%20I.N.D.I.A.%20alliance%2C%20then%20you%20will%20have%20to%20see%20what%20the%20situation%20is%20in%20each%20state.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20there%20is%20a%20fight%20between%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20so%20SP%20should%20be%20supportive%20(of%20Congress).%20They%20had%20only%20one%20MLA%20and%20he%20also%20joined%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%C2%A0Rai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdding%20fuel%20to%20the%20ongoing%20war%20of%20words%20within%20the%20grand%20alliance%2C%20Janata%20Dal-United%20(JDU)%20leader%20and%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20on%20Thursday%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20was%20%26quot%3Bbusy%20with%20the%20state%20assembly%20elections%26quot%3B%20in%20five%20states%20and%20not%20very%20keen%20on%20taking%20the%20I.N.D.I.A.%20bloc%20forward.%20The%20JDU%20is%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20addressing%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India's%20(CPI)%20'BJP%20Hatao%2C%20Desh%20Bachao'%20rally%20in%20Patna%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20we%20constituted%20an%20alliance%20but%20the%20work%20to%20strengthen%20it%20is%20not%20actively%20happening%20right%20now.%20Elections%20are%20about%20to%20happen%20in%20five%20states%20and%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20more%20interested%20in%20that%20it%20seems.%20We%20all%20were%20working%20together%20to%20help%20strengthen%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20take%20it%20forward%20but%20they%20don't%20seem%20to%20be%20as%20keen.%20Congress%20is%20busy%20with%20the%20assembly%20polls%20in%20five%20states%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20asserted%20that%20the%20bloc%20won't%20stop%20the%20fight%20for%20the%20country%20and%20added%20that%20the%20meetings%20of%20the%20coalition%20will%20resume%20once%20the%20elections%20in%20five%20states%20are%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20targeting%20the%20I.N.D.I.A.%20bloc%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20INDI-Alliance%20has%20disintegrated%20before%20it%20is%20formed.%20Now%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20also%20said%20that%20Congress%20does%20not%20care%20about%20other%20parties.%20Even%20before%20this%2C%20one%20can%20see%2C%20that%20Congress%20has%20worried%20about%20Congress%20and%20they%20also%20worry%20about%20families.%20Former%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20is%20only%20busy%20establishing%20her%20son%20and%20daughter%20(Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%202023%20assembly%20elections%20are%20scheduled%20in%20a%20single%20phase%20on%2017%20November%202023.%20The%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%203%20December%20along%20with%20the%20votes%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Mizoram%2C%20and%20Telangana%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699202760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F73piqm5_akhilesh-yadav-ani_625x300_25_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-very-cunning-party-akhilesh-yadav-swipe-on-caste-census-4547970%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20fresh%20attack%20on%20Congress%2C%20its%20ally%20I.N.D.I.A.%20ally%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20accused%20it%20of%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bcunning%26quot%3B%20party%2C%20accused%20it%20of%20%26quot%3Bbetraying%26quot%3B%20him%2C%20and%20urged%20the%20people%20to%20not%20vote%20for%20its%20leaders%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-very-cunning-party-akhilesh-yadav-swipe-on-caste-census-4547970%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-very-cunning-party-akhilesh-yadav-swipe-on-caste-census-4547970%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-very-cunning-party-akhilesh-yadav-swipe-on-caste-census-4547970%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel-Hamas%20conflict%3A%20EAM%20Jaishankar%20speaks%20to%20Iranian%20counterpart%2C%20discusses%20'grave