3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHouse%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson%2C%20a%20devout%20Christian%2C%20once%20blamed%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Roman%20Empire%20on%20%26quot%3Bhomosexual%20behavior.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20credit%20to%20the%20fall%20of%20Rome%20to%20not%20only%20the%20deprivation%20of%20the%20society%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20morals%2C%20but%20also%20to%20the%20rampant%20homosexual%20behavior%20that%20was%20condoned%20by%20the%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said%20in%20a%20radio%20interview%20in%202008%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F11%2F01%2Fpolitics%2Fmike-johnson-kfile-invs%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20CNN%20first%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20claim%20that%20homosexual%20behavior%20brought%20down%20the%20Roman%20Empire%20is%20not%20supported%20by%20historical%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERome's%20collapse%20in%20the%20years%20leading%20up%20to%20AD%20476%20has%20been%20endlessly%20pored%20over%20%E2%80%94%20but%20rarely%20attributed%20to%20its%20sexual%20mores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20common%20factors%20cited%20are%20government%20corruption%2C%20the%20vastness%20of%20the%20territory%20it%20tired%20to%20control%2C%20and%20invasions%20by%20barbarian%20tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20historians%20agree%20that%20same-sex%20sexual%20activity%20was%20tolerated%20and%20even%20accepted%20during%20the%20Roman%20Empire%2C%20although%20there%20were%20still%20some%20taboos.%20The%20main%20activity%20was%20men%20of%20high%20social%20status%20having%20sex%20with%20male%20slaves%20or%20other%20subordinates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Roman%20emperor%20Hadrian%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.liverpoolmuseums.org.uk%2Fantinous-and-hadrian%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehad%20a%20highly%20public%20relationship%20with%20a%20male%20teen%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20ruling%20over%20Rome%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20its%20imperial%20power%20a