s%20split%20between%20the%20two%20districts%20by%20streets.%20The%20houses%20on%20one%20side%20of%20the%20street%20fall%20under%20the%20Rajnandgaon%20constituency%20(Rajnandgaon)%2C%20those%20on%20the%20other%20come%20under%20the%20Durg%20Rural%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20village%2C%20located%20around%2010%20km%20from%20Durg%20town%20on%20the%20Mumbai-Howrah%20National%20Highway-53%20between%20Durg%20and%20Rajnandgaon%20cities%2C%20is%20also%20governed%20by%20two%20panchayats%20--%20Anjora%20village%20panchayat%20(Rajnandgaon)%20and%20Anjora%20'kh%20(B)'%20village%20panchayat%20(Durg).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20interesting%20juxtaposition%20has%20led%20to%20candidates%20from%20Durg%20Rural%20and%20Rajnandgaon%20constituencies%20making%20trips%20to%20Anjora%20for%20canvassing%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20people%20get%20confused%20as%20candidates%20from%20both%20constituencies%20visit%20the%20village%20for%20campaigning.%20Posters%20and%20banners%20of%20candidates%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20entire%20village%20irrespective%20of%20constituencies%20(among%20the%20two)%20from%20which%20they%20have%20been%20contesting.%20It%20is%20said%20the%20village%20elects%20two%20MLAs%2C%26quot%3B%20quipped%20Anju%20Sahu%2C%20sarpanch%20of%20Anjora%20panchayat%20(Rajandgaon%20side).%3Cbr%3E%20Though%20the%20village%20is%20divided%20by%20streets%2C%20people%20here%20have%20coexisted%20peacefully%20and%20celebrate%20festivals%20and%20other%20functions%20together%2C%20said%20Ms%20Sahu%2C%20also%20a%20Congress%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20her%20paternal%20home%20is%20in%20Anjora%20B%20area%2C%20which%20votes%20for%20the%20Durg%20rural%20seat%2C%20while%20her%20in-laws%20vote%20for%20the%20Rajnandgaon%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolling%20to%20the%2090-member%20Chhattisgarh%20assembly%20will%20be%20held%20in%20two%20phases%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rajnandgaon%20is%20among%20the%2020%20seats%20that%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20on%20November%207%2C%20the%20remaining%2070%20constituencies%2C%20including%20Durg%20rural%2C%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20on%20November%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMakhanlal%20Sahu%2C%20husband%20of%20Anjora%20B%20panchayat%20sarpanch%20Sangeeta%20Sahu%2C%20said%20Rajnandgaon%20district%20was%20formed%20in%201973%20after%20being%20carved%20from%20Durg%20district%20(in%20erstwhile%20Madhya%20Pradesh).%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20village%20has%20been%20divided%20into%20two%20panchayats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20delimitation%20for%20assembly%20seats%20was%20also%20done%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20half%20of%20the%20village%20falls%20in%20one%20constituency%20and%20the%20other%20half%20in%20the%20other%20segment%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20such%20families%20in%20the%20village%20whose%20half%20of%20the%20members%20had%20to%20vote%20for%20Rajnandangaon%20constituency%20and%20the%20other%20half%20for%20Durg%20Rural%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20Rajnandgaon%20and%20Durg%20Rural%20are%20prominent%20constituencies%20where%20high-profile%20candidates%20like%20former%20chief%20minister%20Raman%20Singh%20and%20the%20state%20home%20minister%20Tamradhwaj%20Sahu%20are%20in%20the%20fray.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%20has%20fielded%20Raman%20Singh%20from%20his%20incumbent%20Rajnandgaon%20seat%2C%20whereas%20Girish%20Dewanagn%2C%20current%20chairman%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20State%20Mineral%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20is%20the%20Congress%20nominee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Durg%20rural%20seat%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20fielded%20minister%20Sahu%2C%20a%20prominent%20OBC%20leader%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20the%20state%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20a%20new%20face%2C%20Lalit%20Chandrakar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699201740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2Fgatm1bh8_congress-rally-afp_625x300_08_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID