20appeared%20before%20the%20ED%20officials%20in%20Jammu%20on%20Saturday%20at%2010%20am%20and%20was%20allowed%20to%20leave%20the%20agency%E2%80%99s%20office%20in%20the%20late%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShouting%20slogans%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Duggar%2C%20Jai%20Dogra%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CDogra%20Ekta%20Zindabad%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CChoudhary%20Lal%20Singh%20Zindabad%E2%80%9D%2C%20his%20supporters%20gathered%20outside%20the%20ED%20office%20in%20Jammu%20and%20held%20protests%20against%20what%20they%20called%20was%20vindictive%20action%20and%20a%20political%20witch-hunt%20against%20their%20leader.%20Protests%20continued%20throughout%20the%20day%20and%20dispersed%20only%20after%20Lal%20Singh%20was%20allowed%20to%20leave%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20office.%20Singh%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20appear%20again%20before%20ED%20on%20Monday%20(November%206).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20just%20a%20pressure%20tactic%20to%20blackmail%20him%20to%20join%20BJP.%20This%20case%20will%20vanish%20if%20he%20switches%20over%20to%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr.%20Haridutt%20Shishu%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20Lal%20Singh-led%20DSSP%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20questioning%20of%20Singh%20is%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cbrowbeating%20tactics%E2%80%9D%20to%20harass%20candidates%20who%20will%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20party%20in%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20high%20court%20has%20already%20stayed%20the%20re-investigation%20of%20the%20case%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0On%20April%2019%2C%202023%2C%20the%20high%20court%20stayed%20the%20order%20of%20the%20trial%20court%20directing%20re-investigation%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Kanta%20Andotra%2C%20a%20former%20MLA%2C%20said%20that%20BJP%20is%20harassing%20her%20husband%20due%20to%20fear%20of%20their%20defeat%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20are%20they%20harassing%20him%3F%20He%20is%20neither%20chairperson%20nor%20a%20trustee%20of%20the%20RB%20Educational%20Trust%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20mediapersons%20outside%20ED%20office%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20they%20want%20to%20implicate%20him%20in%20a%20false%20case%20to%20stop%20him%20from%20contesting%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%20(organisations)%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20unit%2C%20Ashok%20Koul%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20party%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20ED%20action%20against%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20ED%20says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2018%2C%202023%2C%20the%20ED%2C%20in%20an%20official%20handout%2C%20said%20that%20it%20has%20started%20investigation%20in%20the%20case%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20an%20FIR%20and%20subsequent%20chargesheet%20filed%20by%20the%20CBI%20against%20the%20RB%20Educational%20Trust%20at%20Jammu%2C%20Ajay%20Singh%20who%20was%20the%20then%20District%20Collector%20at%20Kathua%20and%20other%20revenue%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20RB%20Educational%20Trust%20is%20headed%20by%20Lal%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Kanta%20Andotra%2C%20a%20former%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0The%20ED%20claimed%20that%20its%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20the%20Trust%20through%20its%20chairperson%20Kanta%20Andotra%2C%20Lal%20Singh%20and%20other%20trustees%20in%20connivance%20with%20officials%20of%20Revenue%20department%20had%20%E2%80%9Centered%20into%20criminal%20conspiracy%20during%20the%20period%202011%20for%20wrongful%20issuance%20of%20%E2%80%98fards%E2%80%99%20so%20as%20to%20retain%20lands%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20more%20than%20328%20kanals%20in%20favor%20of%20her%20trust%20beyond%20the%20permissible%20limit%20of%20100%20standard%20kanals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Lal%20Singh%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20former%20minister%20and%20two-time%20MP%2C%20Lal%20Singh%20is%20not%20new%20to%20controversies.%20He%20was%20forced%20to%20resign%20as%20minister%20in%20the%20PDP-BJP%20coalition%20government%20in%20April%202018%20over%20his%20participation%20in%20a%20rally%20in%20support%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20gang%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20an%20eight%20-year%20tribal%20girl%20in%20Kathua%20district%20of%20Jammu.%20He%20quit%20the%20BJP%20in%202019%20and%20launched%20his%20own%20political%20party%2C%20the%20Dogra%20Swabhiman%20Sangathan%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20reading%20down%20of%20the%20Article%20370%20and%20reorganisation%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20he%20has%20become%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20BJP%20and%20its%20policies%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20seeking%20special%20constitutional%20safeguards%20for%20Jammuities%20under%20Article%20371%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20started%20his%20political%20career%20as%20a%20student.%20He%20was%20thrice%20elected%20as%20MLA%20from%20Basholi%20assembly%20segment%20of%20Kathua.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20won%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Kathua-Udhampur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%202004%20and%202019%20on%20Congress%20ticket.%20After%20being%20denied%20LS%20ticket%20by%20Congress%20in%202014%2C%20Singh%20joined%20the%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Assembly%20polls%20in%202014.%20He%20won%20the%202014%20Assembly%20election%20on%20BJP%20ticket%20and%20was%20minister%20in%20PDP-BJP%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EED%E2%80%99s%20questioning%20of%20other%20J%26amp%3BK%20politicians%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20also%20questioned%20several%20other%20politicians%20and%20their%20relatives%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENational%20Conference%20president%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Farooq%20Abdullah%2C%20who%20is%20also%20head%20of%20the%20Peoples%20Alliance%20for%20Gupkar%20Declaration%20(PAGD)%2C%20has%20been%20questioned%20multiple%20times%20by%20the%20ED%20since%202019%20in%20connection%20with%20misusing%20funds%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20Cricket%20Association%20(JKCA).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPeoples%20Democratic%20Party%20president%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20and%20her%20mother%20Gulshan%20Nazir%20were%20also%20questioned%20by%20the%20ED%20in%202021%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699196910000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05203638%2FFTB-M7zacAExlKZ.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fformer-minister-lal-singh-enforcement-directorate%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'This%20is%20just%20a%20pressure%20tactic%20to%20blackmail%20him%20to%20join%20BJP.%20This%20case%20will%20vanish%20if%20he%20switches%20over%20to%20BJP%2C'%20Haridutt%20Shishu%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20Lal%20Singh-led%20DSSP%20told%20The%20Wire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fformer-minister-lal-singh-enforcement-directorate%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iran%20Alleges%20Caught%203%20%26quot%3BIsraeli%20Spies%26quot%3B%20In%20Joint%20Op%20With%20Afghanistan%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EState%20television%20in%20Iran%20reported%20on%20Sunday%20that%20three%20Iranians%20it%20said%20were%20agents%20in%20Israel's%20spy%20agency%20Mossad%20have%20been%20detained%20in%20a%20joint%20operation%20with%20Afghanistan's%20Taliban%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bthree%20Mossad%20agents%20who%20held%20Iranian%20nationality%26quot%3B%20were%20detained%20in%20the%20mountainous%20region%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20the%20broadcaster%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENews%20of%20the%20arrests%20came%20after%20a%20Taliban%20delegation%20arrived%20in