%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221059%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECentral%20Park%20in%20the%20fall.%3Cp%3Erabbit75_ist%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETalk%20of%20stock%20market%20seasonality%20tends%20to%20pick%20up%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20and%20for%20good%20reason.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESince%201950%2C%20November%20has%20been%20the%20strongest%20month%20of%20the%20year%20for%20stock%20market%20performance.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20mutual%20fund%20quirk%20could%20be%20driving%20part%20of%20the%20year-end%20seasonality.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20November's%20arrival%2C%20there's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-seasonality-year-end-rally-october-bottom-chart-day-2023-10%5C%22%3Ea%20lot%20of%20talk%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wall%20Street%20about%20stock%20market%20seasonality%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20good%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%201950%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-bottom-outlook-bullish-seasonal-chart-of-the-day-2023-11%5C%22%3ENovember%20is%20on%20average%20the%20strongest%20month%20of%20the%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20stock%20market%20returns%2C%20and%20November%20through%20December%20is%20the%20strongest%20two-month%20period%20on%20average%20for%20returns%2C%20according%20to%20LPL%20Financial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consistent%20stock%20market%20strength%20in%20November%20comes%20shortly%20after%20September%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-weakest-10-day-stretch-sp500-september-seasonal-trends-2023-9%5C%22%3Ewhich%20has%20historically%20been%20the%20worst%20month%20of%20the%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20patterns%20have%20played%20out%20perfectly%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20falling%205%25%20in%20September%2C%20and%20rising%204%25%20in%20the%20first%20few%20days%20of%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20theories%20have%20tried%20to%20explain%20the%20stock%20market's%20seasonality.%20For%20example%2C%20bad%20Septembers%20have%20been%20attributed%20to%20cooler%20weather%20depressing%20sentiment%20among%20traders%20as%20well%20as%20the%20end%20of%20summer%20vacations%20on%20Wall%20Street%20driving%20increased%20selling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20year-end%20strength%2C%20one%20theory%20is%20that%20the%20spread%20of%20holiday%20cheer%20(and%20increased%20spending%20on%20gifts%20by%20consumers)%20encourages%20more%20buying%20than%20selling%20in%20stocks.%20This%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-santa-claus-rally-historical-lpl-says-2020-12-1029918008%5C%22%3Eoften%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BSanta%20Claus%20rally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20one%20driver%20of%20stock%20rallies%20that%20is%20less%20anecdotal%20and%20has%20more%20concrete%20evidence%20to%20back%20it%20up%3A%20a%20quirk%20in%20the%20tax%20code%20for%20mutual%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20mutual%20funds%20have%20until%20October%2031%20to%20make%20their%20tax-loss%20harvesting%20trades%20for%20the%20year%2C%20three%20months%20before%20the%20deadline%20for%20retail%20investors.%20Tax-loss%20harvesting%20is%20a%20trading%20strategy%20to%20lower%20tax%20liability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTax%20loss%20harvesting%20for%20institutional%20investors%20became%20increasingly%20prevalent%20after%20the%20Tax%20Reform%20Act%20of%201986%2C%20which%20mandated%20October%2031%20as%20the%20cut-off%20for%20most%20mutual%20funds%20to%20realize%20capital%20gains%2C%26quot%3B%20Bank%20of%20America's%20Savita%20Subramanian%20explained%20in%20a%20note%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20have%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20markets%20considering%20that%20US%20mutual%20funds%20manage%20more%20than%20%2420%20trillion%20in%20assets%20across%20stocks%20and%20bonds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoss%20harvesting%20involves%20selling%20a%20stock%20that%20has%20suffered%20year-to-date%20losses%2C%20then%20waiting%2030%20days%20to%20buy%20it%20back%20to%20avoid%20the%20wash-sale%20tax%20violation.%20Mutual%20funds%20can%20then%20use%20those%20realized%20losses%20to%20help%20lower%20their%20tax%20liability%20when%20they%20sell%20winning%20stocks%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20historically%20seen%20evidence%20of%20tax%20loss%20selling%20by%20institutional%20investors%20in%20October%20(peak%20outflows)%2C%20and%20by%20retail%20investors%20ahead%20of%20the%20December%2031%20cut-off%20for%20individual%20investors.%20Flows%20for%20both%20groups%20have%20typically%20reversed%20in%20subsequent%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Subramanian%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20that%20reversal%20that%20can%20help%20drive%20stocks%20higher%20into%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20especially%20when%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20year-to-date%20losers%2C%20like%20in%202023.%20While%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20up%20about%2014%25%20this%20year%2C%20about%20half%20the%20companies%20in%20the%20index%20are%20down%2C%20and%20over%20a%20third%20are%20down%20more%20than%2010%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20tax-loss%20candidates%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20move%20higher%20after%20October%2031%2C%20which%20can%20ultimately%20help%20lift%20the%20broader%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%201986%2C%20stocks%20down%2010%25%20or%20more%20from%20January%201%20to%20October%2031%20beat%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20by%201.9%20percentage%20points%20on%20average%20over%20the%20next%20three%20months%20with%20a%2070%25%20hit%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20Subramanian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20mutual%20funds'%20tax-loss%20selling%20now%20in%20the%20rearview%20mirror%2C%20there%20could%20be%20upside%20pressure%20to%20stock%20prices%20as%20mutual%20funds%20start%20to%20buy%20back%20the%20shares%20they%20sold%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20which%20plays%20right%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-baby-rally-year-end-gains-bullish-fundstrat-2023-11%5C%22%3Ethe%20bullish%20year-end%20seasonality.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-november-rally-mutual-fund-tax-loss-selling-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699191001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65454ef936d588dc55cabe37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-november-rally-mutual-fund-tax-loss-selling-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mutual%20funds%20manage%20more%20than%20%2420%20trillion%20in%20assets%2C%20so%20tax-loss%20selling%20in%20late%20October%20could%20drive%20big%20shifts%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20at%20year-end.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-november-rally-mutual-fund-tax-loss-selling-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'This%20is%20genocide'%3A%20Forensic%20teams%20identifying%20Hamas%20victims%20from%20mutilated%20remains%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699190640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F70x70%2Fskynews-israel-tel-aviv-hamas_6349197.jpg%3F20231105134333%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisrael-hamas-war-mutilated-charred-remains-bear-witness-to-the-e