ews%2Fvedanta-confident-to-meet-2-2-billion-debt-obligations-before-march-end-123110500717_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fvedanta-confident-to-meet-2-2-billion-debt-obligations-before-march-end-123110500717_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Clean%20energy%20is%20the%20future%2C%20but%20stocks%20aren't%20acting%20like%20it.%20Here's%20why.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wind%20turbines%20at%20London%20Array%20offshore%20wind%20park%2C%20North%20Sea%2C%20near%20England%2C%20United%20Kingdom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654516da36d588dc55ca476b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221060%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWind%20turbines%20at%20London%20Array%20offshore%20wind%20park%2C%20North%20Sea%2C%20near%20England%2C%20United%20Kingdom.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EClean%20energy%20stocks%20are%20some%20of%20the%20worst%20performing%20stocks%20this%20year%2C%20as%20high%20interest%20rates%20choke%20growth.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Clean%20Energy%20ETF%20is%20down%2034%25%20year-to-date%20and%20companies%20like%20SolarEdge%20are%20down%2070%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EStill%2C%20clean%20energy%20investments%20continue%20to%20grow%20and%20investors%20expect%20performance%20to%20improve.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20growing%20calls%20for%20an%20accelerated%20global%20shift%20to%20clean%20energy%2C%20stocks%20in%20the%20sector%20vastly%20underperforming%20the%20broader%20market.%20In%20fact%2C%20they're%20some%20of%20the%20worst%20performers%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFunds%20that%20track%20clean%20energy%20stocks%20are%20down%20broadly%20in%202023.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Clean%20Energy%20ETF%20and%20the%20iShares%20Global%20Clean%20Energy%20ETF%20are%20down%20more%20than%2030%25%20since%20January.%20Companies%20like%20SolarEdge%20and%20Enphase%20Energy%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20down%2073%25%20and%2067%25%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20paradox%20here%20is%20that%20the%20clean%20energy%20sector%20is%20seeing%20a%20flurry%20of%20investment%2C%20supportive%20policies%20boosting%20new%20projects%2C%20and%20hype%20around%20sustainable%20ventures%20as%20a%20warming%20planet%20drives%20calls%20for%20less%20reliance%20on%20fossil%20fuels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20gives%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F7BrwL%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Clean%20energy%20is%20underperforming%20the%20broader%20market%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20impact%20of%20higher%20rates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFront%20and%20center%20this%20year%2C%20companies%20in%20the%20clean%20energy%20sector%E2%80%93%20like%20companies%20in%20every%20other%20sector%E2%80%94%20are%20being%20pressured%20by%20higher%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Fed%20decided%20to%20pause%20rate%20hikes%20this%20week%2C%20the%20fed%20funds%20rate%20has%20been%20pushed%20up%20at%20a%20historic%20pace%2C%20from%20near%20zero%20in%20March%20last%20year%20to%20a%20range%20of%205.25%25-5.50%25%20currently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20particularly%20tough%20for%20clean%20energy%20companies%2C%20which%20often%20carry%20more%20substantial%20debt%2C%20making%20them%20even%20more%20sensitive%20to%20rising%20rates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20space%20tends%20to%20use%20an%20extraordinary%20amount%20of%20leverage%2C%26quot%3B%20Julien%20Dumoulin-Smith%2C%20a%20research%20analyst%20from%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20a%20surprise%20given%20how%20low-risk%20these%20assets%20tend%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFunding%20in%20the%20debt%20markets%20was%20a%20good%20move%20for%20most%20clean%20energy%20firms%20until%20rates%20began%20to%20soar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20this%20month%20from%20Charles%20Schwab%2C%20analysts%20point%20out%20that%20higher%20rates%20are%20the%20biggest%20hurdle%20for%20many%20of%20these%20stocks%2C%20given%20that%20they%20are%20more%20leveraged%20than%20their%20peers%20in%20the%20traditional%20energy%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHigher%20interest%20rates%20are%20impacting%20these%20companies'%20finances.%20The%20stocks%20in%20the%20MSCI%20World%20Alternative%20Energy%20Index%20have%20a%20leverage%20ratio%20of%203.8%2C%20based%20on%20debt-to-12-month%20earnings%2C%20compared%20with%20just%201.1%20for%20the%20five%20biggest%20energy%20producers%20by%20market%20capitalization.%20That%20means%20higher%20financing%20costs%20are%20much%20more%20costly%20for%20these%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERed%20tape%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20are%20the%20bureaucratic%20hurdles%20to%20getting%20new%20projects%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClean%20energy%20projects%20like%20commercial%20and%20industrial%20solar%20or%20wind%20farms%20need%20to%20clear%20regulatory%20hurdles%20to%20be%20approved.%20And%20right%20now%2C%20sources%20say%20that%20permitting%20process%20is%20slow%2C%20burdening%20the%20build%20out%20of%20clean%20energy%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20projects%20that%20aim%20to%20supply%20renewable%20power%20to%20the%20grid%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20approval%20to%20do%20so.%20That%20list%20of%20requests%20to%20connect%20to%20the%20power%20grid%20is%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Binterconnection%20queue.%26quot%3B%20A%20study%20from%20the%20Lawrence%20Berkeley%20National%20Laboratory%20in%20April%20found%20that%20the%20queue%20was%20so%20long%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bapproximately%20equals%20the%20installed%20capacity%20of%20the%20entire%20US%20power%20plant%20fleet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20poor%20performance%20is%20almost%20directly%20related%20to%20how%20long%20it%20takes%20for%20a%20project%20to%20get%20permitted%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Geoffrey%20Hebertson%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20energy%20market%20intelligence%20firm%20Rystad%20Energy.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20some%20serious%2C%20serious%20concerns%2C%20and%20what%20we're%20noticing%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20project%20delays%20because%20of%20interconnection%20queues%20and%20environmental%20impact%20studies%2C%20which%20are%20all%20incredibly%20important%20and%20needed%2C%20but%20just%20the%20way%20that%20things%20have%20been%20done%20in%20the%20past%20is%20not%20able%20to%20sustain%20all%20of%20this%20growth%20in%20the%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20lagging%20performance%20of%20the%20sector%20can%20also%20be%20chalked%20up%20to%20bad%20timing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20pandemic%2C%20dizzying%20inflation%20and%20broken%20supply%20chains%20sent%20costs%20soaring%20for%20companies%20in%20the%20space.%20Just%20as%20firms%20began%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20supply%20shock%2C%20rates%20went%20up%2C%20putting%20another%20damper%20on%20profitability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20when%20the%20inflation%20wave%20started%20to%20hit%2C%20these%20companies%20were%20very%20much%20hit%20by%20both%20steel%20and%20semiconductor%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20Martin%20Frandsen%2C%20a%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Principal%20Asset%20Management%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20then%20right%20when%20you're%20starting%20to%20catch%20up%20and%20you%20start%20to%20get%20up%20to%20where%20you%20can%20breathe%20again%2C%20then%20comes%20the%20quite%20material%20interest%20rate%20hikes%20on%20top%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20comes%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20high%20interest%20rates%2C%20permitting%20constraints%2C%20and%20supply%20chain%20inflation%20are%20choking%20growth%20in%20the%20renewables%20space%20and%20weighing%20on%20stocks%20in%20the%20sector%20even%20as%20the%20broader%20market%20enjoys%20a%20relatively%20buoyant%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20general%2C%20alternative%20energy%20companies%20are%20what%20we%20call%20'long%20duration'%20stocks%2C%20meaning%20they%20are%20expected%20to%20deliver%20a%20higher%20proportion%20of%20their%20cash%20flows%20in%20the%20more%20distant%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Schwab%20analysts%20wrote%20in%20their%20note.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20clean%20energy%20will%20bounce%20back%2C%20though%20it%20is%20tricky%20to%20know%20when.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20difficult%20thing%20from%20an%20investor%20perspective%20is%20that%20we're%20not%20out%20of%20the%20woods%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Frandsen.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20elements%20which%20have%20negatively%20affected%20these%20green%20stocks%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20interest%20rates%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20inflation%20in%20terms%20of%20cost%2C%20these%20things%20are%20still%20persistent%20and%20there's%20no%20sort%20of%20clear%20sign%20that%20those%20negative%20effects%20are%20going%20to%20evaporate%20any%20time%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComplicating%20that%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20many%20clean%20energy%20companies%20are%20long-term%20investments.%20Rystad's%20Herbertson%20said%20that%20most%20projects%20turn%20a%20profit%20after%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20money%20continues%20to%20pour%20into%20clean%20energy%20and%20investment%20is%20only%20expected%20to%20grow.%20According%20to%20BloombergNEF%2C%20global%20new%20investment%20in%20renewable%20energy%20skyrocketed%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.bnef.com%2Fblog%2Frenewable-energy-investment-hits-record-breaking-358-billion-in-1h-2023%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DRenewable%2520Energy%2520Investment%2520Hits%2520Record%252DBreaking%2520%2524358%2520Billion%2520in%25201H%25202023%2C-August%252021%252C%25202023%26amp%3Btext%3DGlobal%2520new%2520investment%2520in%2520renewable%2Cfor%2520any%2520six%252Dmonth%2520period.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecord-breaking%20%24358%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B24%20and%2025%20looks%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20BofA's%20Dumoulin-Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20practical%20reality%20is%20we're%20looking%20at%20a%20pretty%20reasonable%20recovery%20trajectory%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years%20that%20I%20think%20is%20very%20much%20supported%20by%20the%20%5BInflation%20Reduction%20Act%5D.%20And%20mind%20you%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20not%20even%20just%20the%20IRA%2C%20it%20is%20fundamentally%20that%20the%20demand%20is%20recovering.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frenewable-energy-stocks-climate-change-outlook-performance-interest-rates-markets-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699190101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654516ffb788914e554fc5fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Frenewable-energy-stocks-climate-change-outlook-performance-interest-rates-markets-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22High%20interest%20rates%2C%20regulatory%20hurdles%2C%20and%20inflation%20have%20all%20bogged%20down%20the%20clean%20energy%20sector%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asoni%40insider.com%20(Aruni%20Soni)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Frenewable-energy-stocks-climate-change-outlook-performance-interest-rates-markets-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBhupesh%20Baghel%20Advised%20Me%20To%20Go%20To%20Dubai%2C%26quot%3B%20Claims%20Betting%20App%20Owner%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn