0commodities%2F%20providing%20essential%20services%20and%20all%20LNG%2F%20CNG%2F%20electric%20trucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELight%20Commercial%20Vehicles%20(LCVs)%20registered%20outside%20Delhi%2C%20other%20than%20Electrical%20Vehicles%2C%20CNG%2C%20BS-VI%20diesel%2C%20to%20enter%20Delhi%2C%20except%20those%20carrying%20essential%20commodities%2F%20providing%20essential%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F682343755%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-asd0YNyNE4lFB8loZvui%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.7080062794348508%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22CAQM%20PR%2005.11.2023%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20construction%20and%20demolition%20activities%20have%20been%20banned%20in%20Delhi%20including%20public%20projects%20such%20as%20highways%2C%20roads%2C%20flyovers%2C%20overbridges%2C%20power%20transmission%2C%20pipelines%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20will%20decide%20on%20allowing%20public%2C%20municipal%20and%20private%20offices%20to%20work%20on%2050%20per%20cent%20strength%20and%20the%20rest%20to%20work%20from%20home.%20Central%20Government%20may%20take%20appropriate%20decision%20on%20permitting%20work%20from%20home%20for%20employees%20in%20Central%20Government%20offices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20may%20decide%20to%20discontinue%20physical%20classes%20for%20students%20from%20classes%20six%20to%20nine%20and%20even%20eleven.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelhi-NCR's%20Worsening%20Air%20Quality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20air%20quality%20plummeted%20to%20the%20'severe%20plus'%20category%20again%2C%20making%20the%20national%20capital%20the%20most%20polluted%20city%20in%20the%20country%20today.%20The%20real-time%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20is%20over%20500%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20capital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20noon%2C%20the%20highest%20level%20was%20recorded%20at%20the%20Wazirpur%20monitoring%20station%20in%20Delhi%2C%20reporting%20an%20AQI%20level%20of%20859.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20PM2.5%20concentration%20level%20in%20Delhi%20is%20currently%2096.2%20times%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization's%20(WHO)%20air%20quality%20guidelines%20value.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20PM2.5%20level%20was%20reported%20at%20481%20micrograms%2Fcubic%20metres.%20While%20PM10%20was%20the%20main%20pollutant%20in%20Delhi%20and%20its%20neighbouring%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20air%20quality%20monitoring%20stations%20across%20Delhi%20reported%20a%20PM2.5%20level%20of%20over%20450%20microns.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699188000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-11%2F6iegqjno_delhi-pollution_625x300_02_November_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-bans-entry-of-trucks-construction-activity-as-air-pollution-rises-to-alarming-levels-4547645%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20has%20implemented%20stage-IV%20measures%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%20with%20immediate%20effect%20as%20the%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20and%20its%20neighbouring%20cities%20remains%20in%20the%20'severe%20plus'%20category%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-bans-entry-of-trucks-construction-activity-as-air-pollution-rises-to-alarming-levels-4547645%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-bans-entry-of-trucks-construction-activity-as-air-pollution-rises-to-alarming-levels-4547645%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-bans-entry-of-trucks-construction-activity-as-air-pollution-rises-to-alarming-levels-4547645%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DG