%20was%20open%20to%20looking%20at%20specific%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20Canadian%20authorities%20to%20share%20any.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20told%20the%20Canadians%20saying%20that%20look%2C%20if%20you%20have%20something%20specific%2C%20if%20you%20have%20something%20relevant%2C%20you%20know%2C%20let%20us%20know%20%E2%80%93%20we%20are%20open%20to%20looking%20at%20it%2C%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankar-on-india-canada-diplomatic-row-hardeep-nijjar-killing-room-for-diplomacy-4546206%5C%22%3EJaishankar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20opposite%20number%20in%20Canada%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailyexcelsior.com%2Fcanadian-foreign-minister-joly-says-shes-in-touch-with-her-indian-counterpart%2F%5C%22%3EMelanie%20Joly%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20recently%20said%20that%20they%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20that%20there%20is%20room%20for%20diplomacy%20here.%20I%20know%20that%20my%20counterpart%20in%20Canada%20has%20also%20expressed%20the%20same%20position.%20So%2C%20we%20have%20been%20in%20touch%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20quoted%20Jaishankar%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fglobal-press-views-on-india-canada-row-nijjar-allegations%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Prickly%20Nationalism%E2%80%99%3A%20From%20a%20G20%20High%20to%20a%20Post-Canada%20Low%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20cited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66991662%5C%22%3Esecurity%20threats%20to%20its%20missions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Canada%20when%20it%20suspended%20visa%20services%20in%20the%20country%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20death%20in%20June%2C%20Verma%20was%20named%20in%20a%20pro-Khalistan%20poster%20blaming%20the%20Indian%20government%20for%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20death%20and%20%3Ca%20hr