F05163932%2FScreenshot-2023-11-05-at-4.38.39%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221062%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05163932%2FScreenshot-2023-11-05-at-4.38.39%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201062w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05163932%2FScreenshot-2023-11-05-at-4.38.39%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x112.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05163932%2FScreenshot-2023-11-05-at-4.38.39%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x384.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683572%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22398%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20only%2022%20seats%20that%20the%20Congress%20holds%20with%20a%20margin%20of%20less%20than%2010%25.%20To%20pull%20those%20back%20the%20BJP%20needs%20a%20swing%20of%205%25%20and%20while%20that%20is%20not%20beyond%20the%20realm%20of%20possibility%2C%20since%202018%20was%20its%20worst%20performance%20ever%2C%20even%20those%2022%20seats%20would%20leave%20the%20Congress%20with%20a%20tiny%20majority.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20much%20experience%20in%20reversing%20tiny%20majorities%2C%20so%20the%20big%20question%20will%20be%20whether%20the%20voters%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20are%20displeased%20enough%20with%20the%20Baghel%20government%20to%20move%20decisively%20to%20the%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%2C%20even%20when%20it%20has%20won%2C%20has%20won%20by%20a%20small%20margin%20of%20votes%20that%20has%20given%20it%20benefit%20of%20being%20first%20past%20the%20post.%20Surprisingly%20they%20have%20never%20won%20more%20than%2050%20seats%20or%20got%20more%20than%2041%25%20of%20the%20vote.%20That%20means%20the%20BJP%20needs%20to%20perform%20well%20across%20the%20board%20in%20order%20to%20win%20back%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20anti-incumbency%20will%20hurt%20MLAs%20who%20have%20not%20performed%2C%20that%20may%20not%20by%20itself%20be%20enough%20to%20topple%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80