p%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20word%20came%20that%20October%2031%20was%20celebrated%20by%20state%20authorities%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20%E2%80%98Union%20Territory%20Foundation%20Day%2C%E2%80%99%20I%20must%20confess%20to%20having%20felt%20subjugated%20rather%20in%20a%20colonial%20sort%20of%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20seems%20a%20gleeful%20occupational%20metaphor%20that%20in%20that%20stricken%20part%20of%20the%20nation%20the%20political%20disempowerment%20and%20administrative%20dispossession%20of%20Kashmiris%20should%20become%20an%20occasion%20for%20official%20celebration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0The%20fanfare%20cancelling%20of%20Kashmiris%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9Cbasic%E2%80%9D%20constitutional%20right%20as%20citizens%20of%20the%20republic%20to%20elect%20their%20own%20government%20finally%20gives%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%E2%80%99s%20game%20away%3A%20where%20Article%20370%20was%20to%20be%20understood%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%98temporary%E2%80%99%20arrangement%2C%20Union%20Territory%20status%20and%20benign%20central%20rule%20must%20be%20construed%20as%20permanent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Thus%20a%20curiously%20comedic%20situation%20%E2%80%93%20more%20comedic%20than%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPickwick%20Papers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20confronts%20Kashmiris%3A%20while%20a%20plethora%20of%20political%20organisations%20are%20everyday%20ready%20and%20waiting%20to%20plunge%20into%20an%20enthusiastic%20electoral%20contest%20and%20win%20a%20famous%20victory%2C%20the%20holy%20grail%20is%20missing%20from%20the%20shelf.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20zestful%20wedding%20guests%2C%20as%20it%20were%2C%20dressed%20in%20joyful%20finery.%20But%20no%20wedding%20is%20in%20the%20offing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENor%20does%20it%20seem%20that%20any%20shining%20knight%20on%20a%20white%20steed%20is%20about%20to%20materialise%20to%20restore%20either%20dignity%20or%20representative%20rule%20to%20Kashmiris.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECertainly%2C%20the%20honourable%20Supreme%20Court%20seems%20in%20no%20hurry%20to%20end%20the%20demeaning%20and%20potentially%20damaging%20insult%20and%20denial.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-kashmir-without-elected-government-five-years%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%3A%20In%205%20Years%20Without%20Elected%20Govt%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Crown%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20Has%20Become%20a%20Khap%20Panchayat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKnown%20for%20their%20philosophical%20stoicism%2C%20Kashmiris%2C%20it%20would%20seem%2C%20must%20continue%20to%20plough%20that%20subjective%20resource%20of%20meditative%20sufferance%2C%20and%20ascribe%2C%20as%20they%20often%20do%2C%20their%20circumstance%20to%20god%E2%80%99s%20will.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESmart%20and%20forward-looking%20Kashmiris%20may%2C%20of%20course%2C%20continue%20to%20see%20great%20beauties%20in%20what%20their%20curtailment%20to%20UT%20status%20(the%20only%20Indian%20state%20to%20have%20suffered%20that%20ignominy)%20has%20yielded%2C%20and%20message%20the%20same%20from%20constructive%20television%20shows%20anchored%20by%20Kashmiri%20professionals%20whose%20suspicious%20Urdu%20habits%20have%20now%20been%20suitably%20replaced%20by%20fluent%20nationalist%20Hindi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Other%20%E2%80%98separatist%E2%80%99%20Kashmiris%20had%20thought%20that%20the%20announcement%20of%20elections%20to%20five%20state%20assemblies%20would%20be%20when%20there%20would%20also%20be%20a%20sixth%2C%20namely%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20so%20that%20they%20could%20make%20their%20deleteriously%20democratic%20propaganda%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20forgot%20that%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20continues%20to%20enjoy%20a%20special%20status%2C%20albeit%20not%20of%20their%20imagination.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStill%20others%20speculate%20whether%20such%20special%20status%20may%20not%2C%20after%20all%2C%20be%20conducive%20to%20the%20furtherance%20of%20right-wing%20ambitions%20of%20one-party%20rule%20countrywide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20see%2C%20the%20bad%20example%20of%20Kashmiris%20reinforces%20the%20need%20to%20impose%20the%20good%20example%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20base%20whose%20adoration%20of%20the%20great%20leader%20and%20the%20no-nonsense%20might%20of%20the%20forces%20alone%20ensures%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evishwaguru%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(world%20leader)%20ascendance%20for%20Bharat%20that%20is%20not%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESensible%20Kashmiris%20had%20therefore%20best%20realise%20the%20sterling%20service%20they%20perform%20for%20making%20Bharat%20great%20again%20simply%20by%20agreeing%20to%20be%20made%20a%20naughty%20example%20of.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20seems%20a%20safe%20bet%20to%20assume%20that%20not%20until%20the%20results%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20of%20April%20or%20May%2C%202024%20are%20with%20us%20may%20gentle%20Kashmiris%20know%20what%20is%20in%20store%20for%20them%20constitutionally%20or%20democratically.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETill%20then%2C%20there%20are%20sports%20and%20other%20apolitically%20healthful%20diversions%20that%20Kashmiris%20had%20best%20learn%20to%20embrace%20with%20intelligent%20acceptance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBadri%20Raina%20taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699182060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F19161014%2FScreenshot-2022-10-19-at-4.10.07-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felection-kashmir-ut-foundation-day%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20are%20zestful%20wedding%20guests%2C%20as%20it%20were%2C%20dressed%20in%20joyful%20finery.%20But%20no%20wedding%20is%20in%20the%20offing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felection-kashmir-ut-foundation-day%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Entertainment%20of%20War%20and%20Who%20It%20Is%20Good%20For%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05161727%2FScreenshot-2023-11-05-at-4.15.57.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESaakhi%20is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20about%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%2C%20and%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20may%20try%20hard%20to%20be%20the%20normal%20kind%20of%20working%20woman%2C%C2%A0%20happily%20settled%20down%20in%20a%20sedentary%20job%2C%20available%20for%20the%20family%2024%C3%977%20to%20sort%20out%20household%20affairs%2C%20but%20some%20of%20us%20fail%20to%20achieve%20that%20complete%20calm.%20Perhaps%20the%20stars%20in%20our%20horoscope%20ascertain%20a%20certain%20irresistible%20urge%20to%20pursue%20distant%20dangerous%20shores%20and%20write%20about%20wars%20and%20uprisings.%20Occasionally%2C%20without%20a%20premonition%20of%20trouble%2C%20one%20such%20writer%20may%20land%20in%20areas%20headed%20for%20major%20trouble%20escalating%20into%20wars.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20led%20to%20my%20presence%2C%20purely%20by%20chance%2C%20in%20Jerusalem%20during%20a%20happy%20harvest%20festival%20planned%20with%20old%20friends.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20first%20five%20days%20were%20heavenly%2C%20but%20suddenly%20on%20a%20Sabbath%20morning%2C%20a%20heavy%20and%20sudden%20bombardment%20started%20and%20one%20learnt%20of%20kidnappings%20of%20over%20two%20hundred%20Israelis%20by%20Hamas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20316px)%2085vw%2C%20316px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22316%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22385%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20a%20war%20crime%2C%20one%20learnt%20in%20the%20last%20one%20month.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWar%20is%20a%20crime%20in%20itself.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWar%20enters%20and%20suddenly%2C%20the%20long%20years%20of%20hard%20work%20and%20the%20prosperity%20it%20begat%2C%20get%20rubbed%20off%20by%20an%20unseen%20hand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTell%20us%20about%20how%20you%20felt%20when%20you%20woke%20up%20to%20the%20air%20raid%20sirens%20and%20hid%20in%20safe%20zones%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20What%20was%20it%20like%20to%20be%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20storm%3F%E2%80%9D%20friends%20ask.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETelling%20stories%20about%20a%20war%20is%20hard.%20Even%20more%20hard%20if%20the%20clash%20has%20taken%20place%20between%20two%20historically%20implacable%20enemies%2C%20two%20cultural%20streams.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20know%20from%20the%20start%20it%20is%20doomed%20to%20spread%20with%20dreadful%20swiftness%20and%20infect%20a%20larger%20and%20larger%20area%20as%20old%20historical%20faultlines%20from%20recorded%20ancient%20history%20also%20begin%20to%20heave.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20politically%20sensitive%20seismic%20zones%20in%20the%20world%20where%20East%20meets%20West.%20Where%20most%20of%20the%20major%20conflicts%20between%20the%20two%20cultures%20have%20raged%20since%20the%20Greeks%20and%20the%20Persians%2C%20the%20Assyrians%20and%20Phoenicians.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20did%20those%20human%20tribes%20still%20survive%20multiple%20exterminations%20and%20chaos%20to%20have%20periods%20of%20peace%20and%20prosperity%2C%20only%20to%20one%20day%20tear%20all%20that%20to%20shreds%20in%20another%20bloody%20confrontation%20for%20land%2C%20wealth%20and%20women%2C%20the%20proverbial%20Zar%2C%20Zoru%20and%20Zameen%3F%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20drives%20men%20into%20periodic%20bouts%20of%20madness%20when%20all%20is%20going%20well%3F%20What%20triggers%20it%3F%20Or%20who%3F%20Truth%20be%20told%2C%20till%20Gaza%20happened%2C%20one%20had%20not%20given%20much%20thought%20to%20such%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20wise%20and%20well-travelled%20historian%20Herodotus%20is%20perhaps%20the%20first%20traveler%20turned%20journalist%20who%20recorded%20the%20mother%20of%20all%20East%20West%20clashes%20that%20began%20with%20the%20battle%20between%20the%20Persians%20and%20the%20Greeks.%20But%20wait%2C%20read%20him%20a%20bit%20more%20and%20you%20discover%20it%20was%20not%20a%20madness%2C%20it%20was%20a%20clash%20slyly%20instigated%20by%20the%20Phoenicians%20who%20were%20trader%20merchants.%20They%20triggered%20off%20wars%20between%20kings%20by%20kidnapping%20women%20from%20powerful%20royal%20families%20and%20keeping%20them%20as%20as%20hostages.%20The%20daughter%20of%20the%20Greek%20king%20of%20Argos%20was%20kidnapped%20by%20them%20and%20taken%20as%20captive%20to%20Egypt.%20While%20poor%20Egypt%20was%20sorting%20it%20out%2C%20the%20Greeks%20landed%20in%20the%20Phoenician%20city%20of%20Tyre%20and%20abducted%20Europa%2C%20their%20king%E2%80%99s%20daughter.%20Paris%20of%20Troy%20seized%20Helen%2C%20wife%20of%20the%20Greek%20king%2C%20and%20what%20resulted%20was%20the%20great%20war%20immortalised%20by%20Homer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHomer%20was%20a%20poet%2C%20and%20Herodotus%20an%20objective%20gatherer%20and%20recorder%20of%20the%20factual%20details%20of%20wars%20culled%20from%20various%20sources%20including%20soldiers%2C%20bystanders%20and%20fortune-tellers.%20That%20he%20would%20embellish%20his%20tales%20a%20bit%20was%20understandable%20given%20that%20the%20listeners%20and%20readers%20of%20such%20tales%20also%20want%20what%20Silk%20Smitha%20called%2C%20%E2%80%98Entertainment!%20Entertainment!%20Entertainment!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20450px)%2085vw%2C%20450px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05162025%2FIliad_VIII_245-253_in_cod_F205_Milan_Biblioteca_Ambrosiana_late_5c_or_early_6c-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05162025%2FIliad_VIII_245-253_in_cod_F205_Milan_Biblioteca_Ambrosiana_late_5c_or_early_6c-2.jpg%20450w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05162025%2FIliad_VIII_245-253_in_cod_F205_Milan_Biblioteca_Ambrosiana_late_5c_or_early_6c-2-300x259.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683566%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22389%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIliad%20VIII%20245-253%20in%20codex%20F205%20(Milan%2C%20Biblioteca%20Ambrosiana)%2C%20late%205th%20or%20early%206th%20c.%20ADBy%20Unknown%20author.%20http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lgpn.ox.ac.uk%2Fimage_archive%2Fmss%2Fmss2.html%2C%20Public%20Domain%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcommons.wikimedia.org%2Fw%2Findex.php%3Fcurid%3D4297434%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHerodotus%20lived%20at%20the%20juncture%20of%20two%20ways%20of%20recounting%20history%3A%20the%20written%20one%2C%20which%20was%20slowly%20overtaking%20the%20other%20%E2%80%93%20the%20age-old%20oral%20narration.%20In%20our%20case%20it%20is%20reversed.%20The%20oral%20today%20is%20overtaking%20recorded%20history%20fast%20until%20you%20hardly%20meet%20young%20readers%20and%20researchers%20of%20history%20who%20would%20lend%20a%20teleological%20perspective%20to%20reporting%20about%20wars.%20So%20we%20have%20%E2%80%98Entertainment!%20Entertainment!%20Entertainment!%E2%80%99%20driving%20reporting%20of%20wars%20and%20electoral%20battles%20around%20the%20world.%20In%202023%2C%20Homer%20meets%20TV%20reporters%20talking%20endlessly%20with%20live%20streamed%20visuals.%20For%20lack%20of%20backgrounding%2C%20they%20reduce%20electoral%20battles%20and%20international%20wars%20into%20simple%20binaries%2C%20deciding%20for%20you%20who%20is%20right%20and%20who%20is%20wrong.%20Thus%2C%20war%20becomes%20all%20about%20heroism%20of%20a%20few%2C%20not%20the%20horrible%20blight%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20countless%20civilians%20who%20did%20not%20want%20it%20in%20the%20first%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20war%20begets%20great%20stories%20because%2C%20as%20Herodotus%20knew%2C%20humans%20have%20a%20penchant%20for%20exciting%20tales%20of%20blood%20and%20gore%2C%20love%20and%20lust%2C%20and%20loyalty%20and%20disloyal%20backstabbings.%20But%20being%20a%20self-financing%20reporter%2C%20Herodotus%20remained%20true%20to%20his%20vocation.%20He%20was%20not%20driven%20by%20little%20notes%20or%20texts%20from%20some%20department%20of%20information%20and%20broadcasting.%20He%20travelled%20and%20returned%20for%20his%20popular%20%3Cem%3Edaastangoi%3C%2Fem%3E%20sessions%20about%20war%20in%20various%20cities%20to%20collect%20funds%20for%20his%20next%20trip%20to%20another%20war%20zone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20professional%20principles%20go%2C%20as%20a%20recorder%20of%20history%2C%20Herodotus%E2%80%99s%20first%20principle%20was%20to%20seek%20out%20and%20report%20with%20proof%20who%20lit%20the%20first%20match.%20This%20is%20hugely%20important%20even%20today%20because%20the%20eternal%20law%20for%20revenge%20(%E2%80%98an%20eye%20for%20an%20eye%20and%20a%20tooth%20for%20a%20tooth%E2%80%99)%2C%20still%20prevails.%20And%20revenge%20in%20regions%20where%20wars%20erupt%20again%20and%20again%20is%20not%20simply%20an%20act%20of%20anger%2C%20it%20is%20cherished%20as%20a%20sacred%20obligation%20not%20just%20for%20an%20individual%20family%20but%20the%20entire%20tribe.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%20the%20medieval%20bard%20Chand%20Bardai%20writes%20in%20%3Cem%3EAlha%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EKhand%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20tale%20of%20war%20waged%20in%20far%20off%20Bundelkhand%20region%20in%20India%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EJinke%20dusman%20such%20se%20jeevein%2FUnkey%20jeevan%20ko%20dhikkar!%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20Fie%20upon%20those%20whose%20enemies%20continue%20to%20live%20peacefully%20and%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20law%20of%20Herodotus%20we%20see%20in%20fearful%20clarity%20today%20is%20that%20the%20end%20is%20not%20clear%20from%20the%20outset.%20As%20Solon%20of%20Athens%20told%20the%20super%20rich%20King%20Croesus%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20necessary%20to%20consider%20the%20end%20of%20anything%E2%80%A6because%20God%20often%20offers%20prosperity%20to%20men%20but%20then%20destroys%20them%20utterly%20and%20completely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20rulers%20and%20their%20crony%20capitalist%20friends%20now%20need%20to%20ponder%20over%20this%20law%20of%20Herodotus.%20While%20squandering%20money%20on%20preparing%20for%20mad%20wars%20like%20Napoleon%E2%80%99s%20or%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20and%20nearer%20our%20time%2C%20the%20Soviets%20and%20the%20US%2C%20they%20are%20unraveling%20their%20own%20happiness.%20Their%20transgression%20of%20the%20law%20of%20moderation%20will%20force%20them%20into%20providing%20for%20money%20guzzlers%20more%20boots%20on%20foreign%20soil%2C%20more%20arms%2C%20larger%20monuments%2C%20research%20and%20development%20in%20military%20hardware%2C%20AI%20and%20tech%20spyware.%20Crime%20and%20punishment%2C%20revenge%20and%20justice%2C%20the%20unbreakable%20cycle%20then%20follows%20inexorably.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%20there%20is%20hubris%2C%20the%20royal%20edition.%20The%20rulers%20themselves%20want%20to%20be%20on%20digital%20media%2C%20on%20YouTube%2C%20TikTok%20videos%2C%20and%20vlogs.%20But%20digital%20memory%20will%20evaporate%20with%20time.%20True%2C%20writing%20is%20infinitely%20more%20difficult%20than%20gabbing.%20But%20those%20meticulous%20recorders%20of%20human%20history%20were%20handing%20mankind%20a%20permanent%20legacy.%20They%20were%20waging%20a%20counter%20war%20against%20the%20vital%20lessons%20the%20history%20of%20the%20two%20World%20Wars%20can%20teach%20us.%20Great%20histories%20of%20great%20events%20like%20the%20Partition%20or%20the%201962%20Indo-China%20War%20or%20the%20Bangladesh%20war%20of%20independence%20are%20full%20of%20layers%20and%20minutiae%20that%20may%20help%20recognise%20our%20long%20term%20friends%20and%20enemies%20%E2%80%93%20if%20only%20we%20do%20not%20forget%20what%20actually%20happened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWriting%20about%20Virgil%2C%20T.S.%20Eliot%20cautions%20us%20against%20receding%20into%20what%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%9Cprovincial%20time.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20a%20tendency%20to%20confuse%20wisdom%20with%20knowledge%20and%20knowledge%20with%20information%2C%20and%20then%20trying%20to%20solve%20problems%20of%20life%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20latest%20type%20of%20engineering.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBruce%20Chatwin%2C%20too%2C%20reminds%20us%20through%20the%20wise%20words%20of%20a%20veteran%20of%20the