%20announced%20that%20he%20was%20withdrawing%20the%20publication%20of%20his%20Malayalam%20memoir%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENilavu%20Kudicha%20Simhangal%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(loosely%20translated%20as%20%E2%80%98The%20lions%20that%20drank%20the%20moonlight%E2%80%99).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20reported%20pointed%20out%20certain%20lapses%20regarding%20the%20failure%20of%20Chandrayaan-2.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Somnath%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Fkerala%2F2023%2Fnov%2F05%2Fto-tell-or-not-to-tell-after-kicking-up-controversy-isro-chairman-withdraws-tell-all-memoir-2630153.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20was%20not%20asked%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20withdraw%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20original%20report%20published%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EMalayala%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EManorama%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20excerpts%20from%20the%20book%20which%20suggested%20that%20K.%20Sivan%2C%20the%20former%20ISRO%20chairman%2C%20may%20have%20hindered%20key%20promotions%20that%20Somanath%20thought%20he%20was%20due%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fisro-chairman-somnath-withdraws-memoir-after-controversy%2Farticle67498103.ece%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Somanath%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20some%20misinterpretation.%20At%20no%20point%20have%20I%20said%20that%20Dr.%20Sivan%20tried%20to%20prevent%20me%20from%20becoming%20the%20Chairman.%20All%20I%20said%20was%20that%20being%20made%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Space%20Commission%20is%20generally%20seen%20as%20a%20stepping%20stone%20to%20%5BISRO%E2%80%99s%20chairmanship%5D.%20However%2C%20a%20director%20from%20another%20%5BISRO%20centre%5D%20was%20placed%2C%20so%20naturally%20that%20trimmed%20my%20chances%20%5Bat%20chairmanship%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20officially%20released%20now%20will%20be%20withdrawn%2C%20Somanath%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20book%20isn%E2%80%99t%20officially%20released.%20My%20publisher%20may%20have%20released%20a%20few%20copies%E2%80%A6%20but%20after%20all%20this%20controversy%2C%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20withhold%20publication%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20is%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20interview%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fisro-chief-s-somanaths-remarks-on-ex-boss-sivan-spark-row%2Farticleshow%2F104975210.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20make%20a%20decision%20later%20about%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20release.%E2%80%9D%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20Lipi%20Books%2C%20the%20Kozhikode-based%20publisher%2C%20confirmed%20to%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0that%20it%20was%20withdrawing%20the%20publication.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESomanath%E2%80%99s%20book%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20with%20the%20purpose%20telling%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmotivational%20story%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20personal%20challenges%20he%20faced%20in%20his%20journey%20of%20becoming%20a%20space%20technologist%20and%20in%20executing%20the%20Chandrayaan%20missions%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20not%20to%20create%20controversy.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETOI%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20says%2C%20is%20merely%20160%20pages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20excerpts%20of%20the%20book%2C%20which%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20says%20was%20viewed%20by%20the%20publication%2C%20what%20is%20palpable%20was%20%E2%80%9CSomanath%E2%80%99s%20discomfort%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9CChairman%20%5BDr.%20Sivan%E2%80%99s%5D%E2%80%9D%20decision%20not%20to%20be%20explicit%20about%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-2%20mission.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20was%20a%20software%20glitch%20but%20was%20publicly%20communicated%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinability%20to%20communicate%20with%20the%20lander%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChandrayaan-2%20mission%20was%20originally%20scheduled%20for%20July%2015%2C%202019%2C%20with%20then%20President%20Ramnath%20Kovind%20in%20attendance.%20The%20launch%20was%20called%20off%20an%20hour%20ahead%2C%20due%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%20snag%E2%80%9D.%20Chandrayaan-2%20eventually%20lifted%20off%20on%20July%2022%20but%20the%20Vikram%20lander%2C%20which%20was%20to%20smoothly%20descend%20onto%20the%20moon%20and%20then%20release%20the%20Pragyaan%20rover%2C%20deviated%20from%20its%20planned%20trajectory%20and%20crashed%20on%20the%20moon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20with%20the%20book%20release%20held%20back%20for%20now%2C%20Somanath%20told%20%3Cem%3ETOI%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20plans%20to%20write%20a%20full-length%20autobiography%20after%20retirement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699177591000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F25105326%2FFr_hcepXgAYJgVN.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fspace%2Fisro-ex-chairman-chandrayaan-2-memoir-withdraw-sivan-somnath%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Excerpts%20from%20the%20book%20had%20suggested%20that%20K.%20Sivan%2C%20the%20former%20ISRO%20chairman%2C%20may%20have%20hindered%20key%20promotions%20that%20S.%20Somanath%20thought%20he%20was%20due%20for.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fspace%2Fisro-ex-chairman-chandrayaan-2-memoir-withdraw-sivan-somnath%22%2C%22c