3Emein%20kamal%20humaara%20chehra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(the%20lotus%20is%20our%20face%20for%20the%20campaign).%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20In%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20while%20Raman%20Singh%20and%20Vijay%20Baghel%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eare%20being%20seen%20as%20possible%20chief%20ministerial%20candidates%2C%20for%20now%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20is%20again%20built%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20appeal.%20From%20Bihar%20in%202015%20onwards%2C%20it%20has%20become%20routine%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20pit%20the%20prime-minister%20against%20various%20chief%20ministers%2C%20in%20the%20process%20raising%20the%20stakes%20of%20each%20state%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%E2%80%99%20Differing%20Strategies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20campaigns%20in%20all%20three%20states%20show%20differences%20and%20a%20greater%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Evariety.%20The%20Congress%20in%20Rajasthan%20is%20going%20to%20the%20polls%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20work%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eforegrounding%20some%20path-breaking%20schemes%20for%20development%20and%20welfare.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKaam%20keeya%20dil%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ese%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCongressPhirSe%2Fstatus%2F1718597868649689131%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20phir%20se%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(we%20have)%20worked%20from%20the%20heart%2C%20vote%20the%20Congress%20in%20again)%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eslogan.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlike%2C%20in%202011%2C%20when%20the%20party%20was%20unable%20to%20project%20some%20of%20the%20work%20it%20had%20done%2C%20most%20prominently%2C%20the%20effective%20free%20medicine%20scheme%2C%20Gehlot%20has%20been%20proactive%20in%20publicising%20his%20work.%20A%20highly%20visible%20ad%20campaign%20focused%20on%20the%20development%20schemes%20is%20part%20of%20attempt%20to%20build%20a%20brand%20Gehlot.%20While%20still%20not%20as%20effective%20as%20the%20BJP%20outreach%20it%20is%20a%20great%20improvement%20over%20the%20past.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20NDTV-CSDS-%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fndtv-special-ndtv-24x7%2Fndtv-survey-who-leads-in-pm-modi-vs-ashok-gehlot-battle-in-rajasthan-736382%23video-featured%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELokniti%20poll%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eaired%20on%20November%203%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Gehlot%20government%20had%20an%20approval%20rating%20that%20speaks%20well%20of%20an%20incumbent%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%2043%25%20of%20those%20surveyed%20said%20they%20were%20fully%20satisfied%20with%20the%20Gehlot%20government%E2%80%99s%20performance%20and%2028%25%20were%20somewhat%20satisfied.%20This%20sharp%20focus%20on%20development%20has%20kept%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20campaign%20in%20Rajasthan%20away%20from%20notions%20of%20%E2%80%9Csoft%20Hindutva%2C%E2%80%9D%20unlike%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20even%20Chhattisgarh.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20but%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20Kamal%20Nath%20is%20visibly%20a%20Congress%20politician%2C%20his%20utterances%20could%20easily%20lead%20you%20to%20conclude%20that%20someone%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20or%20maybe%20even%20from%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20had%20been%20picked%20by%20the%20Congress%20as%20its%20CM%20candidate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%E2%80%99%20Kamal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKamal%20Nath%20has%20continued%20to%20reiterate%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20who%20got%20the%20locks%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fkamal-nath-babri-masjid-bjp-hindutva-9010989%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBabri%20structure%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reopened.%20In%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Edoing%20so%2C%20he%20is%20only%20echoing%20a%20stream%20in%20the%20Congress%20that%20has%20expressed%20frustration%20at%20not%20being%20able%20to%20claim%20their%20part%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%C2%A0%20In%20his%20bid%20to%20woo%20the%20Hindu%20vote%2C%20he%20has%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FOfficeOfKNath%2Fstatus%2F1720626842682486930%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eamong%20other%20things%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20promised%20to%20develop%20the%20Sri%20Ram%20Van%20Gaman%20Path%20(the%20route%20believed%20to%20be%20taken%20by%20Ram%20and%20Sita%20during%20their%20exile)%20and%20install%20statues%20of%20Ram%2C%20Nishadraj%20and%20Kewatraj%20in%20Chitrakoot.%20In%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20has%20followed%20suit%20by%20inaugurating%20a%20Ram%20Van%20Gaman%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dbhupesh%2Bbaghel%2Bchhattisgarh%2Bram%2Bgaman%2Bgaman%26sca_esv%3D579379779%26tbm%3Dvid%26source%3Dlnms%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjw0Pqd0KmCAxVA3TgGHb30D0MQ_AUoAnoECAIQBA%26biw%3D1440%26bih%3D789%26dpr%3D2%23fpstate%3Dive%26vld%3Dcid%3Aebd5b30f%2Cvid%3A_VZv-uJVvos%2Cst%3A0%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETourism%20Circuit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20focuses%20on%20the%20sites%20where%20Ram%20and%20Sita%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20stayed%20during%20their%20exile.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20Gehlot%20has%20not%20stayed%20entirely%20clear%20of%20such%20moves.%20His%20setting%20up%20a%20Brahmin%20welfare%20board%2C%20increasing%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fjaipur%2Fhonorarium-of-part-time-priests-hiked-to-5k-per-month%2Farticleshow%2F100290965.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehonorarium%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20priests%20and%20most%20prominently%2C%20his%20allocation%20of%20funds%20for%20gaushalas%20and%20insurance%20for%20cows%20has%20been%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20counter%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20policies.%20But%20in%20his%20speeches%2C%20press-conferences%20and%20in%20this%20election%20campaign%20so%20far%2C%20politics%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Ram%20or%20other%20Hindu%20gods%20has%20been%20kept%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20comparison%20with%20MP%20is%20stark.%20In%20one%20state%20the%20Congress%20is%20hoping%20to%20harvest%20four%20terms%20of%20anti-incumbency%20and%20should%20have%20been%20naturally%20poised%20to%20take%20power%20without%20a%20fight%20yet%20it%20has%20been%20forced%20into%20rhetoric%20that%20has%20never%20helped%20it%20before.%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20governments%20have%20come%20and%20gone%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20five-year%20term%20in%20a%20cycle%20that%20goes%20back%20thirty%20years.%20Yet%2C%20the%20BJP%20remains%20unsure%20of%20a%20victory%20that%20it%20should%20normally%20take%20for%20granted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20this%20lies%20in%20the%20choice%20of%20leaders%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%20is%20an%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20outsider%20to%20MP%2C%20who%20has%20constantly%20had%20to%20foreground%20his%20Hindu%20faith.%20He%20has%20risen%20to%20prominence%20in%20the%20Congress%20primarily%20though%20his%20closeness%20to%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20and%20his%20ability%20to%20organise%20funding.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Gehlot%20is%20an%20OBC%20from%20Rajasthan%20with%20a%20support%20base%20of%20his%20own%20who%20has%20never%20had%20to%20make%20an%20overt%20display%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ehis%20faith.%20These%20differences%20are%20reflected%20in%20the%20campaign.%20Only%20a%20leader%20rooted%20in%20a%20region%20and%20comfortable%20with%20her%20identity%20can%20work%20with%20a%20campaign%20plank%20that%20is%20not%20reactive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20both%20these%20states%2C%20merely%20doing%20well%20in%20the%20state%20elections%20is%20no%20indicator%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eof%20a%20good%20performance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20to%20follow.%20After%20winning%20both%20the%20last%20Assembly%20elections%20the%20Congress%20was%20decimated%20by%20the%20BJP%20with%20its%20emphasis%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20leadership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20try%20and%20ensure%20this%20is%20not%20repeated%20it%20needs%20to%20take%20a%20leaf%20out%20of%20the%20Gehlot%20book%20and%20build%20a%20campaign%20around%20the%20work%20they%20have%20done%20in%20states%20like%20Rajasthan%20and%20Karnataka.%20It%20cannot%20be%20seen%20as%20reacting%20to%20the%20BJP%20with%20soft%20hindutva%2C%20even%20if%20Kamal%20Nath%20wins%20now%2C%20because%20this%20would%20only%20lead%20to%20a%20repeat%20of%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05135822%2FF-GbtyzW0AACY5S.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05135822%2FF-GbtyzW0AACY5S.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05135822%2FF-GbtyzW0AACY5S-300x174.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05135822%2FF-GbtyzW0AACY5S-1024x593.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683548%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22695%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAshok%20Gehlot%20campaigns%20for%20Congress%20in%20Rajasthan.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40ashokgehlot51%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05140137%2FF-JlCywX0AAUpll.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05140137%2FF-JlCywX0AAUpll.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05140137%2FF-JlCywX0AAUpll-300x134.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05140137%2FF-JlCywX0AAUpll-1024x457.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683549%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22536%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20leaders.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40INCMP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Gehlot%20campaign%20also%20has%20repercussions%20for%20Rajasthan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20as%20if%20the%20state%20is%20known%20for%20fiercely%20secular%20politics.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20in%202019%2C%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20aggressively%20speak%20out%20on%20issues%20of%20lynching.%20In%20fact%2C%20tribal%20youth%20rallying%20around%20parties%20like%20BAP%20(Bhartiya%20Adivasi%20Party)%C2%A0%20argue%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20done%20little%20to%20push%20back%20the%20rise%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20allowing%20organisations%20like%20the%20Vanvasi%20Kalyan%20and%20others%20to%20flourish.%20But%20the%20nature%20of%20Hindutva%20politics%20in%20Rajasthan%20does%20not%20share%20the%20tenor%20and%20rhetoric%20of%20the%20Modi%20era.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20Bhairon%20Singh%20Shekhawat%E2%80%99s%20centennial%20celebrations%20in%20Jaipur%20on%20October%2023%2C%20I%20found%20that%20party%20workers%20who%20had%20gathered%20from%20across%20the%20state%20were%20still%20rooting%20for%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20to%20be%20made%20the%20chief%20minister.%20She%20represents%20an%20older%20avatar%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20while%20pushing%20the%20RSS%20agenda%20she%20was%20at%20least%20able%20to%20ensure%20that%20Muslims%20were%20not%20living%20under%20constant%20threat.%20Her%20ability%20to%20keep%20the%20RSS%20in%20check%20was%20already%20in%20decline%20during%20her%20second%20stint%20in%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20BJP%20wins%20soundly%2C%20without%20projecting%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20it%20will%20also%20push%20Rajasthan%20into%20the%20direction%20of%20a%20more%20aggressive%20hindutva.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDifferences%20matter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20the%20current%20state%20of%20the%20country%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ethese%20differences%20matter.%20Today%2C%20we%20look%20across%20the%20opposition%20there%20are%20no%20great%20options%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt.%20In%20this%20otherwise%20bleak%20scenario%2C%20the%20Gehlot%20framework%20at%20least%20provides%20a%20way.%20It%20would%20be%20foolhardy%20of%20the%20party%20to%20forsake%20it%2C%20whatever%20the%20outcome%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699173268000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05135822%2FF-GbtyzW0AACY5S.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-congress-madhya-pradesh-chhattisgarh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20months%20after%20the%20December%20results%2C%20states%20going%20for%20assembly%20elections%20will%20be%20crucial%20battlegrounds%20in%20determining%20the%20shape%20of%20the%202024%20government.%20The%20campaigns%20will%20be%20indicators%20of%20the%20strategies%20the%20two%20parties%20may%20adopt%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-congress-madhya-pradesh-chhattisgarh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Olectra%20Greentech's%20PAT%20nearly%20triples%20to%20Rs%2019%20cr%20in%20Q2%20on%20higher%20revenues%2