ough%20it.%20Revise%20whatever%20you%20have%20mentioned%20and%20have%20answers%20to%20everything%20you%20put%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20go%20unprepared%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Apala%20says%20that%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20myths%20is%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20interview%20round%20as%20it%20will%20only%20test%20your%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20knowledge%2C%20too%2C%20forms%20the%20basis%20of%20our%20personality.%20It%20requires%20equal%20amounts%20of%20work%20that%20one%20puts%20in%20at%20the%20prelims%20and%20mains%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Focus%20on%20what%20you%20know%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281037%2Fhow-to-crack-upsc-interview-tips-ias-officer-twitter-personality-test%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJitin%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%202016-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20says%20that%20having%20confidence%20in%20what%20you%20already%20know%20is%20more%20important%20than%20worrying%20about%20what%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20feel%20underconfident%20imagining%20how%20much%20you%20do%20not%20know.%20Focus%20on%20gaining%20confidence%20from%20how%20much%20you%20already%20know.%20If%20you%20are%20a%20serious%20aspirant%2C%20then%20that%20is%20more%20than%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E15%20Golden%20Tips%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FUPSC%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23UPSC%3C%2Fa%3E%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20Personality%20Test%2FInterview%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%231%20Always%20allow%20the%20interview