%20by%20Modi%20is%20also%20an%20admission%20of%20prevailing%20hunger%20in%20the%20country%2C%20which%20was%20also%20captured%20by%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%202023.%20The%20index%20ranked%20India%20111%20out%20of%20125%20countries%2C%20which%20is%20worse%20than%20its%20neighbours%3B%20Pakistan%20was%20at%20102%2C%20Bangladesh%2081%2C%20Nepal%2069%2C%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20at%2060.%20While%20the%20rate%20of%20undernourishment%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20the%20index%2C%20stood%20at%2016.6%25%20and%20under-five%20mortality%20at%203.1%25%2C%20the%20prevalence%20of%20anemia%20in%20women%20aged%20between%2015%20and%2024%20years%20stood%20at%2058.1%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20release%20of%20the%20index%2C%20in%20the%20second%20week%20of%20October%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20rejected%20the%20index%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20%E2%80%98methodological%20issues%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20had%20described%20the%20ranking%20given%20to%20India%20as%20%E2%80%9Cerroneous%20and%20having%20malafide%20intent%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20women%20and%20child%20development%20minister%2C%20Smriti%20Irani%2C%20had%20dismissed%20the%20index%20by%20making%20remarks%20which%20opposition%20parties%20described%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmockery%20of%20hunger%E2%80%9D%20and%20called%20out%20her%20%E2%80%9Cinsensitivity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20that%20makes%20headlines%20now%2C%20many%20a%20people%20have%20said%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20hogwash.%20How%20do%20they%20build%20that%20indice%3F%203%2C000%20people%20in%20a%20country%20of%20140%20crore%20get%20a%20phone%20call%20from%20Gallup%20and%20they%20are%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%98Are%20you%20hungry%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20then%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%20trust%20me%2C%20I%20have%20left%20my%20house%20in%20Delhi%20in%20the%20morning%20at%204%20today.%20I%20got%20a%20flight%20at%205%20to%20go%20to%20Kochi.%20I%20did%20a%20conclave%20there.%20Got%20a%20flight%20at%205%20o%E2%80%99clock%20to%20come%20to%20this%20programme.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20get%20to%20anything%20called%20food%2C%20it%20will%20be%2010%20o%E2%80%99clock.%20If%20you%20would%20have%20called%20me%20anytime%20during%20the%20day%20today%20and%20asked%20from%20Gallup%2C%20%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20hungry%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%E2%80%99ll%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9COh%20yes%2C%20I%20am.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%20this%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fglobal-hunger-index-smriti-irani-gallup-poll%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Epiece%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20explains%20why%20Irani%E2%80%99s%20assertions%20on%20the%20hunger%20index%20are%20misleading.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPM%20Modi%20has%20been%20attacking%20Opposition%20parties%20on%20what%20he%20has%20termed%20%E2%80%98revdi%20culture%E2%80%99%C2%A0%20but%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20hit%20back%2C%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fnews%2Felections%2Fprasad-if-distributed-among-public-paap-if-given-to-own-friends-kejriwals-fresh-counter-to-pms-revdi-remark-5597923.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDelhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20saying%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20people%20are%20talking%20about%20revdi.%20When%20revdi%20is%20distributed%20among%20the%20public%20for%20free%2C%20then%20it%E2%80%99s%20called%20%E2%80%98prasad%E2%80%99%20%5Bdevotional%20offering%5D.%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9Cis%20given%20for%20free%20to%20your%20own%20friends%2C%20ministers%2C%20then%20it%20is%20%E2%80%98paap%E2%80%99%20%5Bsin%5D%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20An%20earlier%20version%20of%20this%20piece%20had%20misrepresented%2080%20crores%20in%20million.%20The%2