.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04134759%2FSunita-who-died-on-November-2.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04134759%2FSunita-who-died-on-November-2-300x260.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04134759%2FSunita-who-died-on-November-2-1024x887.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683483%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221039%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThirteen-year-old%20Sunita%20died%20on%20November%202.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20Manupotai%20and%20Sunita%2C%20many%20people%20in%20the%20Adivasi-dominated%20Bastar%20region%20have%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%20However%2C%20these%20people%20have%20been%20facing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fchhattisgarh-christians-hindutva-communalism%5C%22%3Eincreasing%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20other%20villagers%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fjanjati-suraksha-manch-to-hold-rallies-demanding-de-listing-of-converted-tribals-from-the-st-list%2Farticle66642111.ece%5C%22%3Ebacked%20by%20Hindutva%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20equate%20Adivasi%20customs%20and%20traditions%20with%20the%20Hindu%20religion%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20prohibit%20non-Hindu%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20government%20changes%20(after%20these%20elections)%2C%20it%20will%20be%20good%20if%20they%20listen%20to%20everyone.%20All%20we%20want%20from%20this%20election%20is%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20government%20supports%20everyone%20else%2C%20they%20should%20support%20us%20as%20well%20and%20listen%20to%20our%20problems.%20We%20have%20rights%20but%20we%20are%20not%20getting%20them%20in%20our%20villages.%20They%20should%20ensure%20our%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manupotai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20348px)%2085vw%2C%20348px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22348%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22287%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESanturam%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Dev%20Samiti%20that%20looks%20after%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20religious%20affairs%2C%20said%20the%20Christians%20must%20come%20back%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Emool%20dharma%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9C.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20stay%20in%20Sanatan%20Dharma%2C%20then%20you%20are%20violating%20%3Cem%3Edharam%20reeti%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5Breligious%20customs%5D.%20We%20want%20our%20village%20to%20follow%20proper%20customs%20and%20traditions.%20%3Cem%3EDev%20reeti%3C%2Fem%3E%20needs%20to%20be%20followed%20in%20the%20village.%20I%20am%20not%20opposing%20anyone.%20They%20are%20our%20brothers%20and%20sisters.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20come%20back%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Emool%20dharma%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20come%20back%20to%20our%20%3Cem%3Edev%20reeti%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20is%20what%20PESA%20also%20allows.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20phase%20of%20elections%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20on%20November%207.%20Twelve%20of%20the%2020%20constituencies%20going%20to%20the%20polls%20fall%20in%20the%20tribal%20belt%20of%20the%20Bastar%20division.%20Narayanpur%2C%20which%20will%20vote%20on%20November%207%2C%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20claims%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fraipur%2Fmass-conversions-in-chhattisgarh-under-congress-govt-amit-shah%2Farticleshow%2F103315610.cms%5C%22%3Eforced%20conversions%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20by%20Christian%20missionaries%20in%20the%20tribal%20regions%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fraipur%2Fmass-conversions-in-chhattisgarh-under-congress-govt-amit-shah%2Farticleshow%2F103315610.cms%5C%22%3Ealleged%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20wave%20of%20religious%20conversions%20has%20been%20unleashed%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20state%20under%20the%20Bhupesh%20Baghel-led%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20called%20these%20allegations%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-ts-singh-deo-bhupesh-baghel-chhattisgarh%5C%22%3Ebaseless%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20no%20issues%20to%20highlight%20and%20was%20hence%20polarising%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAftermath%20of%20the%20Narayanpur%20church%20attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fprotests-in-chhattisgarhs-narayanpur-over-coordinated-anti-christian-violence%5C%22%3E20%20instances%20of%20anti-Christian%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20reported%20from%20the%20Narayanpur%20district%20in%20December%20last%20year%20alone%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThings%20came%20to%20a%20boil%20at%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20new%20year%20when%20the%20Sacred%20Heart%20church%20inside%20the%20Viswadeepti%20High%20School%20in%20Narayanpur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiancurrents.org%2Farticle-catholic-church-vandalised-in-chhattisgarh-ic-correspondent-1497.php%5C%22%3Ewas%20vandalised%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20January%202%2C%202023.%20The%20attack%20took%20place%20shortly%20after%20the%20police%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20tribal%20community%20over%20religious%20conversions%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20took%20place%20while%20the%20school%20was%20in%20session%2C%20with%20children%20inside%20the%20premises.%20The%20incident%20resulted%20in%20a%20police%20officer%20being%20injured.%20Following%20the%20attack%2C%20five%20individuals%2C%20including%20BJP%20district%20president%20Rupsai%20Salam%2C%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFather%20Jomon%20Devasia%2C%20the%20pastor%20of%20the%20church%20and%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20school%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20in%20his%20four%20years%20of%20working%20in%20Narayanpur%2C%20he%20had%20never%20anticipated%20such%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20church%20is%20now%20being%20rebuilt.%20However%2C%20scars%20of%20the%20attack%20remain%2C%20with%20several%20glass%20windows%20still%20damaged%20and%20yet%20to%20be%20fixed.%20It%20used%20to%20be%20a%20place%20visited%20by%20hundreds%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04134904%2FWhere-Mother-Mary-statue-was-stood-inside-Viswadeepti-School-vandalised-during-attack-yet-to-be-reinstalled.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04134904%2FWhere-Mother-Mary-statue-was-stood-inside-Viswadeepti-School-vandalised-during-attack-yet-to-be-reinstalled.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04134904%2FWhere-Mother-Mary-statue-was-stood-inside-Viswadeepti-School-vandalised-during-attack-yet-to-be-reinstalled-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683484%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Mother%20Mary%20statue%20inside%20Viswadeepti%20School%20was%20vandalised%20during%20the%20attack.%20It%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20reinstalled.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20day%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20Devasia%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20told%20me%20that%20there%20was%20a%20meeting%2C%20so%20don%E2%80%99t%20come%20out%20of%20the%20premises.%20They%20came%20near%20the%20church%20and%20started%20pelting%20stones.%20They%20were%20chanting%20in%20Gondi%20%3Cem%3Emaaro%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bhit%5D%20and%20barged%20into%20the%20church.%20About%20200-300%20people%20entered%20the%20church%2C%20but%20at%20least%20a%20thousand%20were%20standing%20outside%20the%20gate.%20All%20the%20teachers%20and%20I%20gathered%20the%20children%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20police%20and%20let%20them%20out%20to%20their%20parents%20from%20the%20field%20behind%20the%20church.%20The%20children%20did%20not%20have%20to%20see%20any%20of%20the%20violence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20his%20church%2C%20which%20falls%20under%20the%20Jagdalpur%20Diocese%2C%20has%20been%20providing%20services%20to%20hospitals%20and%20schools%20for%20over%20five%20decades%20in%20seven%20districts.%20However%2C%20during%20this%20period%2C%20he%20has%20never%20seen%20any%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20politics.%20We%20are%20here%20only%20to%20spread%20education%20through%20our%20schools%20and%20help%20people%20through%20our%20hospitals.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20to%20us%20which%20party%20is%20in%20power%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20away%20from%20the%20district%20centre%20and%20inside%20Narayanpur%E2%80%99s%20villages%20in%20the%20dense%20forest%20areas%2C%20villagers%20are%20paying%20the%20price%20for%20their%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fislam-christianity-conversion-hindutva-violence%5C%22%3ENo%20Country%20for%20Religious%20Converts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20March%206%2C%20the%20elder%20brother%20of%20Santernag%2C%20aged%2036%2C%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%20in%20Sulenga%20village.%20Like%20Monupatai%2C%20Santernag%20(32)%20brought%20his%20sibling%E2%80%99s%20body%20back%20home%20from%20the%20hospital%20and%20wanted%20to%20bury%20him.%20However%2C%20about%20five%20to%20six%20people%20prevented%20the%20family%20from%20accessing%20the%20burial%20ground%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20would%20only%20allow%20it%20if%20the%20family%20followed%20traditional%20Adivasi%20customs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20there%20was%20a%20ground%20inside%20the%20village%20where%20we%20%3Cem%3EVishwasis%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bas%20Christians%20are%20commonly%20referred%5D%20could%20bury%20our%20dead.%20But%20now%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20allow%20us%20to%20do%20so.%20We%20even%20asked%20the%20police%20to%20intervene.%20I%20have%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20these%20villagers%2C%20which%20is%20still%20underway.%20Finally%2C%20my%20brother%20was%20buried%20in%20the%20Christian%20burial%20ground%20near%20the%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04135002%2FSanternag-in-his-house-in-Sulenga-village.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04135002%2FSanternag-in-his-house-in-Sulenga-village.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04135002%2FSanternag-in-his-house-in-Sulenga-village-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683485%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESanternag%20in%20his%20house%20in%20Sulenga%20village.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESarita%2C%2024%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Kokodi%20village%2C%20has%20been%20boycotted%20by%20her%20family%20for%20adopting%20Christianity%20in%202012.%20Her%20parents%20died%20when%20she%20was%20young.%20She%20lives%20in%20her%20family%20home%2C%20while%20her%20brother%20and%20his%20family%20moved%20out.%20Standing%20outside%20her%20house%2C%20Sarita%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20she%20goes%20to%20work%20in%20different%20villages%2C%20doing%20odd%20jobs%20for%20other%20Vishwasis%20in%20their%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20brother%20is%20not%20a%20Vishwasi%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20talk%20to%20me%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20me.%20He%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20me%20to%20work%20on%20the%20family%20land.%20The%20villagers%20have%20put%20pressure%20on%20him%20to%20not%20have%20any%20ties%20with%20me.%20They%20have%20asked%20him%20to%20convince%20me%20to%20leave%20Christianity%2C%20but%20I%20refused.%20They%20struck%20my%20name%20off%20the%20MGNREGA%20rolls%2C%20so%20I%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20go%20outside%20the%20village%20and%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESarita%20said%20that%20her%20parents%20had%20taken%20her%20to%20church%20after%20a%20long%20bout%20of%20illness%20when%20she%20was%20young.%20After%20meeting%20several%20doctors%20and%20going%20to%20hospitals%2C%20she%20said%2C%20it%20was%20when%20she%20went%20to%20the%20church%20that%20she%20started%20getting%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20say%20that%20we%20have%20started%20following%20the%20church%20because%20we%20got%20money%20or%20someone%20forced%20us.%20But%20it%20is%20nothing%20like%20that.%20I%20have%20become%20a%20Vishwasi%20because%20it%20helped%20me%20during%20my%20illness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJunai%2C%20who%20also%20lives%20in%20the%20same%20village%20as%20Sarita%2C%20said%20that%20she%20too%20adopted%20the%20church%E2%80%99s%20ways%20after%20a%20lump%20on%20her%20foot%20became%20infected.%20She%20said%20she%20tried%20all%20kinds%20of%20treatments.%20She%20was%20advised%20by%20some%20Vishwasis%20to%20visit%20the%20church%20and%20after%20she%20went%20there%20and%20started%20praying%2C%20her%20leg%20became%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWithin%20a%20week%20of%20praying%20and%20applying%20coconut%20oil%2C%20my%20leg%20became%20better%20so%20I%20started%20praying%20regularly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04135103%2FSarita-and-Junai-outside-Saritas-house-in-Kokodi-village.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04135103%2FSarita-and-Junai-outside-Saritas-house-in-Kokodi-village.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04135103%2FSarita-and-Junai-outside-Saritas-house-in-Kokodi-village-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683486%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESarita%20and%20Junai%20outside%20Sarita%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Kokodi%20village.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CGive%20us%20our%20rights%20and%20a%20separate%20burial%20ground%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20force%20here.%20We%20have%20adopted%20the%20Christian%20faith%20because%20of%20our%20own%20free%20will%20and%20our%20beliefs%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Santernag.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20we%20want%20is%20that%20land%20should%20be%20allotted%20for%20Vishwasis%20from%204-5%20nearby%20villages%20to%20bury%20our%20dead%20with%20dignity.%20The%20Congress%20has%20assured%20us%20that%20if%20they%20come%20to%20power%2C%20they%20will%20give%20us%20a%20ground.%20But%20if%20the%20BJP%20comes%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20much%20hope.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20these%20villagers%20who%20are%20struggling%20to%20give%20a%20dignified%20burial%20to%20their%20loved%20ones%2C%20all%20they%20want%20from%20this%20election%20is%20an%20assurance%20of%20their%20rights%20being%20enforced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEither%20they%20should%20let%20us%20bury%20on%20our%20own%20land%20or%20they%20should%20give%20us%20land%20in%20every%20village%20for%20Vishwasis%20to%20bury%20our%20dead.%20Congress%20is%20saying%20that%20they%20made%20a%20mistake%20%5Bby%20not%20enforcing%20their%20rights%5D%20but%20we%20will%20help%20you%20this%20time.%20But%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20said%20any%20such%20thing.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20another%20government%20like%20the%20Congress%20which%20will%20make%20empty%20promises.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20fear%20that%20there%20will%20be%20violence%20if%20the%20BJP%20comes%20to%20power%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Manupotai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20I%20want%20is%20that%20we%20should%20not%20be%20boycotted%20like%20this%20or%20stopped%20from%20working.%20We%20should%20be%20able%20to%20live%20in%20our%20villages%20peacefully%20and%20not%20be%20stopped%20from%20working%20in%20MGNREGA%20and%20other%20government%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sarita.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04135217%2FManupotai.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04135217%2FManupotai.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04135217%2FManupotai-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683487%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManupotai.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConversion%20a%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20issue%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20villagers%20are%20paying%20the%20price%20for%20the%20bogey%20of%20%E2%80%9Cconversions%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20in%20the%20district%20have%20pointed%20fingers%20at%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChandan%20Kashyap%2C%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20from%20Narayanpur%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20sitting%20MLA%2C%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20only%20talking%20about%20%E2%80%9Cforced%20conversions%E2%80%9D%20as%20it%20has%20no%20other%20issues%20to%20highlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlease%20ask%20the%20BJP%20where%20all%20churches%20have%20been%20made%20and%20how%20many%20conversions%20took%20place%20during%20its%2015-year%20rule%20in%20the%20state.%20Ever%20since%20the%20Baghel%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%202018%2C%20there%20have%20been%20no%20conversions%3B%20instead%2C%20%3Cem%3Evikas%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bdevelopment%5D%20has%20happened.%20They%20have%20no%20issues%20to%20show.%20They%20did%20not%20do%20anything%20for%20Adivasis%20and%20now%20they%20are%20talking%20about%20conversions.%20But%20we%20have%20written%20off%20loans%20for%20farmers%2C%20we%20are%20buying%20paddy%20at%20over%20Rs%202%2C600%20per%20quintal.%20This%20is%20why%20this%20conversion%20issue%20that%20they%20are%20claiming%20will%20not%20affect%20these%20elections.%20We%20have%20built%20roads%2C%20schools%2C%20hospitals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20an%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20Narayanpur%20in%20January%20but%20we%20also%20took%20action%20immediately.%20That%20whole%20incident%20was%20pre-planned%20by%20the%20BJP.%20If%20the%20government%20had%20not%20acted%20then%2C%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20lives%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20saved%2C%20police%20officers%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20beaten%20up.%20They%20have%20no%20issue%20to%20fight%20elections%20on%20and%20that%20is%20why%20in%20the%20Adivasi%20belt%2C%20those%20who%20converted%20earlier%20are%20being%20targeted.%20Let%20them%20show%20what%20work%20they%20have%20done%20in%20the%2015%20years%20they%20were%20in%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERupsai%20Salam%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20vandalism%20of%20the%20church%20in%20Narayanpur%20in%20January%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20conversion%20is%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConversion%20is%20not%20just%20an%20issue%20for%20BJP%20but%20a%20social%20issue.%20Adivasi%20conversion%20is%20a%20big%20social%20issue.%20Congress%20is%20saying%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20doing%20this%2C%20but%20this%20is%20a%20social%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ealso%20reached%20out%20to%20Kedar%20Kashyap%2C%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20from%20Narayanpur%2C%20but%20did%20not%20get%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699086593000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04135514%2FSacred-Heart-Church-rebuilt-after-the-vandalism-in-January.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-adivasi-christians-struggle-conversion-bogey-narayanpur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Narayanpur%2C%20which%20will%20vote%20on%20November%207%2C%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20BJP's%20claims%20of%20%26quot%3Bforced%20conversions%26quot%3B%20by%20missionaries%20in%20the%20tribal%20regions%20of%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-adivasi-christians