ocumenting%20both%20the%20momentous%20and%20regular%20moments%20in%20Indian%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20certain%20magic%20to%20the%20pictures%20he%20captured%20as%20if%20stealing%20a%20moment%20in%20time%20from%20his%20subject%E2%80%99s%20life.%20As%20he%20once%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20photography%20are%20slices%20of%20human%20life%2C%20gentle%20and%20personal.%20Their%20aim%20is%20to%20let%20the%20viewer%20see%20all%20by%20himself.%20They%20tend%20not%20to%20preach%2C%20not%20to%20pose%20as%20art.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESatyan%20always%20emphasised%20that%20his%20pictures%20were%20not%20the%20result%20of%20encounters%20between%20events%20and%20him%20but%20rather%20a%20witness%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290133%2Fkerala-photographer-sharun-recreates-raja-ravi-varma-paintings-with-trans-models%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einteresting%20moments%20in%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20he%20met.%20%E2%80%9CPhotography%20has%20enabled%20me%20to%20save%20them%20from%20vanishing%20into%20thin%20air%20and%20to%20give%20them%20a%20life%20of%20their%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20many%20iconic%20moments%20he%20covered%20were%20the%20merger%20of%20Pondicherry%20with%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20in%201954%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ESatyagraha%3C%2Fem%3E%20against%20Portuguese%20rule%20in%20Goa%20during%20the%201950s%2C%20Pope%20Paul%20VI%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20India%20in%201964%2C%20and%20the%20smallpox%20eradication%20campaign%20organised%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20between%201961%E2%80%9363.%20In%201977%2C%20he%20was%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F283077%2Fwoman-quits-law-labour-child-birth-photography-unconventional-jobs-mommy-story%2F%5C%22%20targe