%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20they%20ferry%20people%20with%20disability%20free%20of%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20informs%20that%20any%20lost%20items%20in%20the%20auto%20are%20returned%20to%20the%20police%20station%20or%20the%20customer%20directly.%20Arijit%20Chatterjee%2C%20who%20left%20his%20belongings%20in%20an%20auto%2C%20managed%20to%20retrieve%20them%20the%20following%20morning%2C%20even%20though%20he%20did%20not%20have%20the%20driver%E2%80%99s%20or%20the%20auto%E2%80%99s%20license%20plate%20number%20as%20he%20hailed%20the%20auto%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20seen%20the%20%E2%80%98Smart%20City%20Auto%20Association%E2%80%99%20mentioned%20on%20the%20auto%20when%20I%20got%20off.%20So%20when%20I%20realised%20I%20had%20left%20my%20cards%20in%20the%20auto%2C%20I%20came%20across%20another%20auto%20with%20the%20same%20logo%20and%20told%20its%20driver%20what%20happened.%20He%20immediately%20informed%20the%20leader%20of%20their%20group%20who%20broadcasted%20the%20message%20in%20their%20circle.%20The%20auto%20driver%20who%20had%20ferried%20me%20called%20me%20within%20a%20few%20hours%20and%20handed%20over%20the%20valuables%20at%20my%20office%20the%20next%20morning%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arijit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAuto%20drivers%20turned%20social%20workers%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fautoo-1698927036.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Auto%20drivers%20from%20Bhubaneswar%20ferry%20accident%20victims%20to%20the%20nearest%20hospitals%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fautoo-1698927036.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fautoo-1698927036-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fautoo-1698927036-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fautoo-1698927036-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fautoo-1698927036-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333433%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAuto%20drivers%20from%20Bhubaneswar%20ferry%20accident%20victims%20to%20the%20nearest%20hospitals.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EDinabandhu%20remembers%20the%20initial%20days%20when%20no%20one%20was%20willing%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20him.%20Eventually%2C%2020%20drivers%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20frame%20of%20mind%20of%20the%20drivers%20then%20was%20very%20different.%20They%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20think%20of%20any%20benefit%20in%20joining%20me.%20They%20thought%20that%20they%20were%20doing%20just%20fine.%20More%20than%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20people%20I%20approached%20said%20no%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Slowly%2C%20as%20drivers%20started%20seeing%20the%20changes%20implemented%20by%20the%20small%20group%2C%20they%20turned%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDinabandhu%20emphasises%20that%20he%20focused%20on%20enhancing%20driver%20safety%2C%20curbing%20the%20exploitative%20practices%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98mafia%E2%80%99%20that%20demanded%20exorbitant%20fees%20from%20drivers%20for%20parking%20at%20stands%2C%20and%20consequently%2C%20he%20gained%20respect%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288854%2Ftamil-nadu-auto-driver-daughter-tops-board-exams-after-fathers-heart-attack%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrivers%20within%20the%20city%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20association%E2%80%99s%20system%20is%20different.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20extort%20money%20to%20park%20in%20stands.%20We%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20fighting%20and%20that%20no%20one%20lifts%20a%20finger%20among%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20more%20and%20more%20drivers%20came%20around%20when%20they%20saw%20that%20he%20was%20indeed%20changing%20the%20status%20quo.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVenkat%20Senapathy%2C%20one%20of%20the%20founding%20members%20of%20the%20association%2C%20says%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20their%20problems%20were%20solved%20thanks%20to%20Dinabandhu%E2%80%99s%20initiative.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20major%20problems%20was%20parking%20at%20the%20auto%20stand.%20We%20faced%20many%20difficulties%20with%20the%20Police%20too.%20Dinabandhu%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20took%20care%20of%20these%20issues.%20And%20now%20we%20have%20access%20to%20many%20facilities%20and%20feel%20good%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20social%20initiatives%2C%20Dinabandhu%20focused%20on%20bringing%20about%20behavioural%20change%20among%20auto%20drivers.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20the%20drivers%20were%20counselled%20and%20educated%20against%20bad%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20spoke%20to%20the%20drivers%20and%20told%20them%20not%20to%20drink%20and%20drive.%20If%20we%20find%20anyone%20driving%20drunk%2C%20we%20remove%20them%20from%20our%20association.%20The%20act%20of%20returning%20lost%20items%20to%20customers%20has%20also%20improved%20our%20image%20among%20the%20Police%2C%20who%20earlier%2C%20used%20to%20be%20frustrated%20with%20the%20drivers.%20Now%2C%20they%20listen%20to%20us%20and%20even%20call%20us%20for%20any%20emergency%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dinabandhu%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20glad%20that%20the%20public%20opinion%20has%20changed%20from%20negative%20to%20positive.%20The%20drivers%20provide%20their%20numbers%20at%20hospitals%20and%20blood%20banks%2C%20and%20also%20collect%20surplus%20food%20from%20weddings%20and%20other%20big%20events%20to%20distribute%20among%20the%20needy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20the%20pandemic%20struck%20the%20state%2C%20the%20auto%20drivers%20stepped%20up%20to%20serve%20people.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20ferried%20people%20for%20free%2C%20took%20patients%20to%20hospitals%2C%20and%20also%20carried%20oxygen%20cylinders.%20We%20pooled%20in%20for%20the%20medical%20treatment%20of%20drivers%20who%20fell%20sick.%20Unfortunately%2C%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20considered%20COVID%20warriors%20and%20the%20Government%20didn%E2%80%99t%20help%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dinabandhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20informs%20that%20the%20driver%20group%20assisted%20their%20peers%2C%20covering%20medical%20expenses%20and%20immediate%20necessities%20for%20the%20families%20of%20drivers%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20because%20of%20COVID.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20driver%20Deepak%20Sethi%20says%20that%20they%20feel%20satisfied%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20because%20they%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20help%20others.%20He%20adds%20that%20people%20see%20them%20in%20a%20different%20light%20today%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20him%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20we%20are%20not%20seen%20as%20only%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247298%2Flaibi-oinam-first-woman-auto-driver-manipur-documentary-meena-longjam-national-award-non-feature-covid-19-inspiring-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrivers%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20as%20social%20workers%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20Dinabandhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698931991000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fauto1-min-1698752031.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333311%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dinabandhu%20Nayak%20started%20the%20Smart%20City%20Online%20Auto%20Association%20for%20Bhubaneswar's%20auto%20drivers%20-%20who%20now%20return%20lost%20belongings%2C%20give%20free%20rides%20to%20the%20