ation%20in%20the%20house%20as%20cavities%20act%20as%20thermal%20insulators%20providing%20warmth%20in%20winter%20and%20cool%20air%20in%20summer.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20have%20ACs%20or%20air%20coolers.%20During%20summers%2C%20usually%2C%20the%20interior%20temperature%20is%20at%20least%20seven%20degrees%20cooler%20than%20outside%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20repurposed%20old%20wood%20for%20%3Cem%3Ehaveli%3C%2Fem%3E-type%20ambience%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20buying%20new%20wooden%20furniture%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20opted%20to%20source%20antique%20wooden%20doors%2C%20planks%2C%20and%20staircases%20from%20demolished%20homes%20within%20the%20city.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20repurposed%20old%20glass%20doors%20from%20restaurant%20refrigerators%20to%20craft%20elegant%20glass%20window%20doors.%20Furthermore%2C%20they%20used%20cycle%20rims%20to%20create%20unique%20window%20frames%20%E2%80%94%20showcasing%20their%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20and%20resourcefulness%20in%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20construction%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20reused%20two%20truckloads%20of%20old%20wood%20in%20the%20construction.%20The%20old%20wood%20gives%20a%20typical%20old%20%3Cem%3Ehaveli%3C%2Fem%3E-type%20ambience%20to%20our%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20harvest%20sunlight%20and%20rain%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20ago%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20installed%20an%20off-grid%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F269780%2Fmy-zero-waste-home-saves-70-energy-by-using-the-sun-to-run-appliances%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20power%20system%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20a%20capacity%20of%20one%20kilowatt%20to%20fulfil%20the%20household%E2%80%99s%20essential%20energy%20requirements.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20family%20has%20succ