0chemical-free%20home%20products%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20has%20implemented%20a%20greywater%20treatment%20system%2C%20which%20effectively%20repurposes%20treated%20greywater%20from%20kitchen%20sinks%2C%20basins%2C%20and%20bathrooms%20for%20watering%20the%20plants%20in%20their%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20encountered%20a%20foul%20smell%20coming%20from%20nearby%20tanks%2C%20mostly%20from%20the%20accumulated%20dirty%20water.%20We%20realised%20that%20the%20smell%20was%20mostly%20because%20of%20the%20various%20oils%20and%20chemical%20detergents%20we%20used%2C%20which%20polluted%20the%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20this%20set%20them%20to%20start%20another%20exciting%20experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20chemical%20cleaners%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20started%20making%20natural%20cleaners%20using%20a%20blend%20of%20bio%20enzymes%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20and%20wood%20ash.%20To%20create%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332396%2Fhow-to-make-bio-enzymes-from-kitchen-waste-at-home-diy-steps-by-kolkata-gardener-nita-singh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebio%20enzymes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20collects%20flowers%20and%20lime%20waste%2C%20adding%20natural%20ingredients%20such%20as%20fenugreek%2C%20coconut%2C%20rice%2C%20aloe%20vera%2C%20black%20seeds%2C%20and%20hibiscus.%20These%20elements%20are%20combined%20to%20make%20powerful%20shampoos%2C%20body%20washes%20and%20liquid%20cleaners%20for%20washing%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20completely%20stopped%20purchasing%20detergents%20from%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThroughout%20these%20years%2C%20the%20father-son%20duo%20embarked%20on%20their%20transformative%20journey%20without%20a%20clear%20plan.%20Rather%2C%20each%20experiment%20served%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20the%20next%2C%20leading%20to%20several%20com