uce%2C%20Manish%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EManish%20led%20a%20group%20of%20farmers%20to%20form%20the%20Jardalu%20and%20Katarni%20Agro%20Producer%20Company%20Limited%2C%20a%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisation%20(FPO)%2C%20in%20April%202023.%20Their%20journey%20was%20made%20possible%20through%20the%20support%20of%20Bayer%2C%20working%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Small%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Agri-Business%20Consortium%20(SFAC)%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20developed%20the%20concept%20of%20FPOs%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20to%20enable%20small%20and%20marginal%20farmers%20to%20improve%20their%20access%20to%20investments%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20markets.%20The%20power%20of%20collectivisation%20not%20only%20improved%20production%20efficiency%20but%20also%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20better%20pricing%20strategies%20and%20marketing%20avenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20farmers%20become%20self-reliant%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-scaled.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bayer%20nurtures%20and%20guides%20FPOs%20in%2021%20states%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-scaled.jpeg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-1536x11