re%E2%80%99%20(MBE)%20in%201983%2C%20and%20the%20Sanctuary%20Asia%20Lifetime%20Service%20Award%20in%202013.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20what%20strikes%20out%20the%20most%20to%20me%20is%20her%20ability%20to%20forge%20alliances%20over%20common%20cause%20across%20an%20incredibly%20diverse%20set%20of%20people%20and%20stakeholders%20%E2%80%94%20from%20forest%20officers%20to%20politicians%20in%20high%20offices%3B%20from%20businessmen%20to%20communities%20living%20around%20forests%3B%20from%20celebrities%20and%20global%20and%20national%20public%20figures%20to%20young%20school%20kids%3B%20and%20from%20naturalists%20to%20policymakers.%20She%20worked%20with%20everyone%20and%20brought%20them%20together%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20conservation%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Raza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20think%20of%20very%20few%20people%2C%20perhaps%20none%2C%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20conservation%20history%20who%20single-handedly%20worked%20over%20such%20a%20long%20period%2C%20over%20so%20many%20states%2C%20and%20with%20so%20many%20diverse%20sets%20of%20peoples%20and%20interests%20in%20such%20harmony%2C%20and%20brought%20about%20such%20remarkable%20results.%20And%20of%20course%20who%20can%20forget%20the%20power%20of%20her%20pen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRazaKazmi17%2Fstatus%2F1710262197698310376%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERaza%20Kazmi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Wildlife%20Protection%20Society%20of%20India%20(WPSI)%2FFacebook%20and%20Kipling%20Camp%2FFacebook)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698676639000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAnne-Wright-Final-Feature-Image-05-1698675652.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333222%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%